1
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:37,030
顾问! 我找到他了!
Counselor! I've got him!

2
00:03:39,710 --> 00:03:44,238
下来!你下来!
Down! You come down!

3
00:03:50,788 --> 00:03:52,619
马上下来吧!
Down for good!

4
00:03:57,195 --> 00:03:59,493
抱歉这么早打扰您.
Forgive this early intrusion.

5
00:03:59,931 --> 00:04:01,057
你好啊
How are you?

6
00:04:01,566 --> 00:04:04,660
我一直都很仰慕您. 很荣幸见到您.
I am a great admirer of yours. Honored to meet you.

7
00:04:05,503 --> 00:04:06,470
可以么?
May l?

8
00:04:07,572 --> 00:04:10,405
我可以用下打字机么, 先生?
Can I use your typewriter, sir?

9
00:04:10,775 --> 00:04:14,506
你的手臂，放松.
Your arm, please. Relax it.

10
00:04:15,079 --> 00:04:19,311
- 年龄? - 43.
- Your age? - 43.

11
00:04:21,085 --> 00:04:22,882
那么，您的下一部作品是什么?
So, what are you cooking up?

12
00:04:23,421 --> 00:04:25,286
又是一部没劲的戏?
Another film without hope?

13
00:04:25,423 --> 00:04:27,448
－第一次治疗么? －是啊
- First time taking the cure? - Yes.

14
00:04:30,528 --> 00:04:31,620
深呼吸
Take a deep breath.

15
00:04:33,297 --> 00:04:34,286
请进
Come in.

16
00:04:36,267 --> 00:04:39,361
- 对不起.我待会儿再来吧 - 没关系，进来吧
- I'm sorry. I'll come back later. - No, do come in.

17
00:04:39,804 --> 00:04:40,828
吸气
Breathe in.

18
00:04:43,507 --> 00:04:44,474
深吸气
Deeper.

19
00:04:46,777 --> 00:04:49,678
早上好啊...我能吸烟么?
Good morning... May I smoke?

20
00:04:53,918 --> 00:04:55,180
咳嗽
Cough.

21
00:04:57,588 --> 00:04:58,486
呼气
Breathe in.

22
00:05:00,491 --> 00:05:02,584
- 您读过了吧 - 是的
- You've already read it? - Yes.

23
00:05:03,828 --> 00:05:04,920
吐气
Breathe.

24
00:05:07,732 --> 00:05:09,199
那么...您怎么看?
And... what do you think?

25
00:05:11,202 --> 00:05:14,763
嗯，我记了东西，一会儿给你看
Well, I made some notes, but we'll talk later.

26
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:19,601
你身体有点疲劳 可以穿上衣服了
Your system is a bit worn out. You may get dressed now.

27
00:05:21,345 --> 00:05:23,836
这姑娘看起来还行啊，是美国人吧
Nice looking girl. American, right?

28
00:05:24,415 --> 00:05:26,440
你够专业的了
You've got some fine merchandise there.

29
00:05:26,617 --> 00:05:28,414
这个治疗对您的病很有帮助， 你会很快恢复的
This treatment will do you good, you'll see.

30
00:05:29,687 --> 00:05:32,656
护士，300毫升清水
Nurse. 300 ml of holy water,

31
00:05:32,790 --> 00:05:38,558
空腹15分钟后，吃3 片
3 doses to be taken at 1 5 minute intervals, on an empty stomach.

32
00:05:38,696 --> 00:05:42,154
- 隔一天清洗一次 - 什么时间了?
- Mud bath every other day... - What time is it?

33
00:05:42,433 --> 00:05:46,426
泥疗后十分钟，在处方上的药水里泡十分钟
After the mud bath, ten minutes in the mineral water as prescribed...

34
00:05:47,138 --> 00:05:50,335
我在温泉那等你 好，谢谢你了
- I'll wait for you at the spring. - Yes, thank you.

35
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,192
先生!
Sir!

36
00:09:04,668 --> 00:09:06,431
您的杯子
Sir, your glass.

37
00:09:17,948 --> 00:09:18,915
在这呢
Over here.

38
00:09:20,451 --> 00:09:22,749
您想聊聊那部电影么? 那太好啊
You want to talk about the film? - Yes, of course.

39
00:09:22,786 --> 00:09:27,450
好的.那就是说， 你想让制作人也看到我的意见么
Fine. Just tell me if you'd like the producer to see my report.

40
00:09:27,491 --> 00:09:31,018
放心，我不会给您添麻烦的
Frankly, I wouldn't want to be the one to cause you any trouble.

41
00:09:31,095 --> 00:09:33,359
别担心 让你来就是要听你的意见么
No, don't worry. I'm the one who called you in.

42
00:09:33,731 --> 00:09:35,892
首先，我觉得这部片子
On first reading it's evident

43
00:09:35,966 --> 00:09:40,835
缺少矛盾冲突， 或者说铺垫的还不够
that the film lacks a problematic, or a philosophical premise...

44
00:09:40,971 --> 00:09:42,302
要坐下聊吗?
Would you like to sit down?

45
00:09:42,373 --> 00:09:46,173
...整体上这部片子没有连贯性
...making the film a series of gratuitous episodes,

46
00:09:46,710 --> 00:09:51,044
影片重点放在非现实主义
perhaps amusing for their ambiguous realism.

47
00:09:51,849 --> 00:09:55,046
会让人觉得主题还不够突出
One wonders what the authors are trying to say...

48
00:09:55,186 --> 00:09:57,950
这是一部让人联想的片子呢? 或者是惊栗?
Are they trying to make us think? To scare us?

49
00:09:58,556 --> 00:10:03,550
影片的开端，就显得缺乏灵感
From the start, the action reveals a poverty of poetic inspiration.

50
00:10:04,528 --> 00:10:07,986
希望您别介意，让我来解释一下原因
Forgive me, but this might be the definitive proof

51
00:10:08,065 --> 00:10:14,061
影片的手法有点落后
that cinema is 50 years behind all other arts.

52
00:10:14,138 --> 00:10:17,130
主题显得有些没有意义
The subject doesn't even have the merits

53
00:10:17,174 --> 00:10:21,474
这部片子，确实需要改改
of an 'avant garde' film, but it has all the shortcomings.

54
00:10:21,745 --> 00:10:25,511
看看我的笔记，也许会有点帮助
Here, my notes. I doubt they will be helpful.

55
00:10:27,885 --> 00:10:31,912
我还是有点不敢相信您会考虑我的意见
It's still a mystery that you'd think of me

56
00:10:31,989 --> 00:10:36,016
从合作的角度来讲，老实说 我觉得您不会考虑
for a collaboration that, frankly, I don't think can work.

57
00:10:36,460 --> 00:10:39,759
不，绝对不.相反，这对我很有帮助
No, no. On the contrary. You'll be most helpful.

58
00:10:40,631 --> 00:10:45,568
你看看，这部片子... 我真的很想拍出来
You see, the film... I really want to make this film.

59
00:10:45,636 --> 00:10:48,799
我推迟两个星期拍就是因为...
I postponed the shoot for two weeks because...

60
00:10:54,678 --> 00:10:57,238
马责柏塔! 你说什么?
Mezzabotta! Pardon me.

61
00:11:01,018 --> 00:11:03,543
马责柏塔! 马里奥! 你也来了?
Mezzabotta! Mario! You're here too?

62
00:11:04,221 --> 00:11:05,381
贵度!
Guido!

63
00:11:09,560 --> 00:11:11,391
你这是怎么了?
What happened to you!

64
00:11:12,196 --> 00:11:14,596
嘿，老贵度，最近怎么样?
Hey, big Guido, how are you?

65
00:11:14,665 --> 00:11:18,066
你也开始长白头发了，老了啊!
You've sprouted quite a few white hairs, old Snaporaz!

66
00:11:18,502 --> 00:11:20,663
你又喝这个? 对你不好的!
Are you drinking that stuff? It's bad for you.

67
00:11:20,838 --> 00:11:25,002
他们说我的肝...唉 你这是治什么呢?
They said my liver is, well... And you, what's your treatment?

68
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:29,946
等一下...珂劳迪亚!
Just a second... Gloria!

69
00:11:30,381 --> 00:11:34,750
你女儿.已经成人了啊 哦，她不是我女儿
- Your daughter. She's all grown up. - No, she's not my daughter.

70
00:11:36,020 --> 00:11:40,423
残忍的蜜蜂，吸食了花朵美丽的生命
Cruel bees, sucking all the life from these poor flowers.

71
00:11:41,091 --> 00:11:45,084
亲爱的，这是我的朋友... 对不起，我这鞋...
- Darling, this is my friend... - I'm sorry. My shoes...

72
00:11:46,096 --> 00:11:48,428
珂劳迪亚，珂劳迪亚 莫仁 你好
Gloria. Gloria Morin. - Nice to meet you.

73
00:11:49,533 --> 00:11:50,500
你好
Fine, thank you.

74
00:11:50,868 --> 00:11:54,395
我认识你，你的爸爸常常提起你
I know all about you. Pupi always, always tells me.

75
00:11:54,972 --> 00:11:58,931
我们还因为评论你的上一部片子大吵一架呢
We even had a big fight when I was very critical of your last film.

76
00:11:59,109 --> 00:12:00,872
是啊.我们真的很喜欢看
That's not true. You liked it a lot.

77
00:12:02,513 --> 00:12:04,777
去喝点东西吧，走
Let's go for a drink. Let's go.

78
00:12:06,984 --> 00:12:09,214
你一个人来得么? 你夫人呢?
And you, are you here alone? And your wife?

79
00:12:09,286 --> 00:12:10,685
是啊，一个人来的 一个人多好
- Yes, I'm alone. - Better that way...

80
00:12:11,055 --> 00:12:13,182
哈哈，还是这样好啊
Well, I mean, better in general...

81
00:12:14,325 --> 00:12:16,759
你听说我和蒂娜的事了吧 谁是蒂娜?
You heard about Tina and me? - Tina?

82
00:12:17,194 --> 00:12:19,458
我们在等着宣誓
We're waiting for an annulment.

83
00:12:20,064 --> 00:12:22,624
所以我们都来了. 我们已经订婚了
That's why we're here together. We're engaged.

84
00:12:24,068 --> 00:12:25,228
恭喜你们!
Congratulations.

85
00:12:25,636 --> 00:12:28,469
哈哈，老贵度.你在忙什么呢?
Well, big Guido. What are you working on? Something good?

86
00:12:28,806 --> 00:12:31,036
我在想找一个世外桃源让我静一静
Sure is the ideal place to do some thinking.

87
00:12:31,108 --> 00:12:33,736
丹米尔，我就是作者，这位小姐... 对不起，改怎么称呼你?
Daumier, the author, Miss... Pardon me, what is your name?

88
00:12:33,811 --> 00:12:35,244
珂劳迪亚 莫仁
- Gloria. - Gloria Morin.

89
00:12:36,213 --> 00:12:38,875
见到你很高兴! 我非常欣赏您的作品
Nice to meet you. I am a big admirer of yours.

90
00:12:38,949 --> 00:12:40,416
过奖了!
I'm flattered.

91
00:12:41,118 --> 00:12:44,610
你是演员么? 我好像在那见过你的照片
Are you an actress? Did I see your photo somewhere?

92
00:12:44,722 --> 00:12:47,190
演员.是的, 嗯...
An actress. Yes, well...

93
00:12:47,257 --> 00:12:52,058
我确实想过. 而且野心还不小
I have ambitions in that area. Actually enormous ambitions,

94
00:12:52,129 --> 00:12:54,324
不过也只是想想而已
but that's all, for the moment.

95
00:12:54,465 --> 00:12:55,762
她可是哲学毕业的哦
She's got a degree in philosophy.

96
00:12:55,833 --> 00:12:57,926
见到你是我的荣幸.马里奥 很高兴见到你
Allow me. Mario Mezzabotta. - Nice to meet you.

97
00:12:58,001 --> 00:13:01,960
我还没拿到文凭. 我正在写篇论文，有点不一样的论文
I don't have a degree. I'm doing my thesis. It's a bit different.

98
00:13:02,039 --> 00:13:04,667
在写什么? 是很难的那种
- And the subject? - A difficult one.

99
00:13:05,075 --> 00:13:08,875
是探讨男性在现代生活当中的孤独
The loneliness of modern man in contemporary theater.

100
00:13:09,246 --> 00:13:10,941
听起来不错，对吧，专家
Interesting subject. Right, Professor?

101
00:13:11,682 --> 00:13:14,879
要反映点什么呢? 是反复无常的幻觉么
And what is the meaning of the capricious apparitions

102
00:13:14,918 --> 00:13:16,715
来体现女性存在的意义
of the girl of the spring?

103
00:13:16,987 --> 00:13:19,922
很纯洁的题材 主题很有亲和力
An offer of purity? Of warmth to the protagonist?

104
00:13:19,957 --> 00:13:24,553
所有我见过的题材中 很明显，这是最糟的了
Of all your story's overabundant symbols, this is the worst...

105
00:14:12,743 --> 00:14:14,938
希望她写不出来，最好是写不出来!
She didn't make it. Better that way.

106
00:14:35,632 --> 00:14:38,965
别废话了，你怎么样? 还好吧
- Yack! How are you? - Not too bad.

107
00:14:39,036 --> 00:14:41,061
有人认识你么? 我想不是吧
- Did anybody recognize you? - I don't think so.

108
00:14:41,104 --> 00:14:42,696
这些包都是你的么?
You brought all that luggage?

109
00:14:42,739 --> 00:14:46,175
有5个箱子 衣服就有好多
It's just five suitcases. Gowns occupy so much space.

110
00:14:46,243 --> 00:14:48,905
我带来一个...给你看看 全是你带来的?
I brought one... you'll see. Did you get it all?

111
00:14:48,979 --> 00:14:53,040
珂尔拉，这里晚上很安静的 什么活动都没有
Carla, it's quiet here at night. There's nothing going on.

112
00:14:53,116 --> 00:14:56,574
这么时髦的地方 一定有节目的
But it's a fashionable spa. There must be some fashion shows,

113
00:14:56,653 --> 00:14:58,917
有些酒吧很热闹的啊，酒店里就有
some trendy clubs, even at our hotel.

114
00:14:59,990 --> 00:15:01,685
你去看看了么? 是啊
Have you been behaving? - Yes, yes.

115
00:15:01,758 --> 00:15:04,625
可是...我的酒店里已经满了
Actually... I couldn't get you a room in my hotel,

116
00:15:04,695 --> 00:15:07,664
而且酒店里的人都认识我
and besides it's full of people who know me.

117
00:15:07,898 --> 00:15:10,924
这样吧，我来安排个地方 找个好点的...
So, I found someplace else. A perfect hotel...

118
00:15:11,101 --> 00:15:13,433
那倒不错，可是... 为什么要这样?
Very pretty, you know... - But why?

119
00:15:14,871 --> 00:15:18,602
这小子是谁? 斯古么?呵呵
- And how's this guy? - Sgulp? Great.

120
00:15:20,277 --> 00:15:21,744
你脸色不太好，怎么了?
You look a little pale. How come?

121
00:15:22,613 --> 00:15:24,808
就是这，我说的就是这
See, the hotel is right here.

122
00:15:26,984 --> 00:15:29,282
斯格诺拉，房客
Signora, guests!

123
00:15:29,353 --> 00:15:31,617
我就说么，也很一般...
See. Like I told you. It's not...

124
00:15:31,822 --> 00:15:33,983
这里也很安静啊.你不是饿了么
but it's very quiet. If you're hungry,

125
00:15:34,057 --> 00:15:36,184
我去叫点三明治的来
I'll get them to bring a couple of sandwiches.

126
00:15:36,259 --> 00:15:40,218
这给我感觉不太好 没有拉，这也不错
It feels a little sad here. - No, it's typical!

127
00:15:40,530 --> 00:15:42,555
我当然饿了. 你都吃过午餐了，我还没呢
Besides I'm hungry. You had lunch, but I didn't.

128
00:15:42,833 --> 00:15:44,232
你好，先生
Hello, Sir.

129
00:15:46,336 --> 00:15:47,394
单人房间舒服么
How's the solitaire coming along?

130
00:15:47,471 --> 00:15:49,439
什么都有的，有单独的卧室和洗手间
Everything's ready, the room, the bathroom.

131
00:15:49,506 --> 00:15:51,838
放心休息吧 斯格诺拉会象在家一样舒服的
Rest assured. Signora will feel at home.

132
00:15:51,908 --> 00:15:54,468
好的，谢谢你.有什么吃的么?
Yes, thank you. You wouldn't have anything ready for lunch?

133
00:15:54,544 --> 00:15:56,102
休息室里就有 就在这边
- The restroom, please? - It's over there.

134
00:15:56,179 --> 00:15:58,306
我自己去就可以了
I'll see to it personally.

135
00:15:59,149 --> 00:16:01,913
真不好意思. 我的手好脏啊
Trains, such horrible things. They leave your hands so black.

136
00:16:03,053 --> 00:16:04,748
我来了你不高兴么 当然高兴
Are you happy I'm here? - Yes.

137
00:16:05,255 --> 00:16:08,224
是一点点还是很开心 特别的开心
- Really happy or a little happy? - Very happy.

138
00:16:08,792 --> 00:16:10,191
嗯，不错
Hmm. Smack!

139
00:16:11,128 --> 00:16:12,595
你笑起来真甜
Mm, what a nice smell!

140
00:16:12,729 --> 00:16:16,165
贵度，这绒面一定会很皱起来的
Guido, I thought this black velvet was going to wrinkle.

141
00:16:16,233 --> 00:16:19,134
是吗?好，好 不，不会皱的
- Really? Good, good. - But no. Not a wrinkle.

142
00:16:19,403 --> 00:16:20,995
坐三个小时都不会皱的
Even after a three-hour trip.

143
00:16:26,576 --> 00:16:30,205
你还没说喜不喜欢呢 觉得怎么样?
You didn't even tell me you like it. Do you like it?

144
00:16:30,347 --> 00:16:32,110
你穿上更漂亮了
Such a beautiful lady!

145
00:16:35,352 --> 00:16:38,082
她戴着很优雅
So refined. That thing she has on her head...

146
00:16:38,155 --> 00:16:39,144
这是什么? 舒服么?
What is it? Ploosh?

147
00:16:39,222 --> 00:16:41,918
舒服，舒服，哦，还不错
- Plush, plush. - Ah, ploosh.

148
00:16:43,293 --> 00:16:46,694
我就是要找这个呢 真是踏破铁鞋呀
I looked around for it like crazy. I was quite desperate.

149
00:16:47,597 --> 00:16:50,225
你真了解我啊 当珂尔拉后悔的时候...
But you know me. When Carla makes up her mind...

150
00:16:50,367 --> 00:16:52,164
好了，好了
- Snarp! - Sgulp!

151
00:16:53,103 --> 00:16:55,264
我上周读了一个唐那得的故事
I read a good Donald Duck last week...

152
00:16:55,305 --> 00:16:56,966
有一只恐龙
There was a dinosaur...

153
00:16:57,007 --> 00:17:00,408
她就在这，我的宝贝屁屁 正经点，一只恐龙...
- Here she is, my sweet-buns. - Be good, a dinosaur...

154
00:17:00,444 --> 00:17:04,642
贵度正经点 你想知道什么
Guido be good. What do you want to do now?

155
00:17:04,881 --> 00:17:07,509
你肯定会出席么? 当然了，为什么问这个?
Are you sure you've been behaving? - Sure, why?

156
00:17:07,684 --> 00:17:12,644
随便吧，我已经饿了 哦，我的结婚戒指
Anyway, now sweet-buns is hungry. Oh, my wedding ring.

157
00:17:12,856 --> 00:17:15,916
听着，贵度. 你可答应过我的...
Listen, Guido. That little thing you promised me...

158
00:17:16,159 --> 00:17:17,387
答应什么了?
What little thing?

159
00:17:18,495 --> 00:17:21,828
我打赌她一定要说她丈夫的事了
Now I bet she brings up her husband again.

160
00:17:22,365 --> 00:17:25,801
你不觉得么? 看着吧!老家伙
You don't think so? You'll see, old Snaporaz.

161
00:17:27,571 --> 00:17:30,131
可怜的，她看起来一点也不开心
My poor Luigi doesn't seem happy at all.

162
00:17:30,674 --> 00:17:33,700
你看，我丈夫一点都不自信
You see, my husband is not the confident type.

163
00:17:34,211 --> 00:17:36,202
他只是有点沮丧
He gets depressed.

164
00:17:36,646 --> 00:17:39,843
他一点都不笨，还很聪明的
He's not stupid, you know. He's actually very clever...

165
00:17:40,250 --> 00:17:42,275
呜啊，这儿好热
It's so hot here!

166
00:17:43,420 --> 00:17:45,650
他对罗马的历史了如指掌
He knows all of Roman history by heart.

167
00:17:46,089 --> 00:17:48,489
他只需要一点点的帮助
He just needs a push.

168
00:17:48,692 --> 00:17:50,956
他在石油公司上班，只有那么一点点薪水
He's still working at the fuel company, same salary.

169
00:17:51,061 --> 00:17:51,959
是么
Really?

170
00:17:52,496 --> 00:17:54,794
快把钱包给我 别弄花了
Be good and put down my purse. You'll break it.

171
00:17:54,831 --> 00:17:58,130
我很喜欢这个钱包 是他给我的
I love that little purse. He gave it to me.

172
00:17:59,970 --> 00:18:02,268
你怎么不帮他找份别的工作
Why don't you find him a job?

173
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:06,905
你交际广 而且也答应过我的啊
You know so many people. You've promised it so many times.

174
00:18:07,544 --> 00:18:10,274
我曾经梦到过
I even had a dream about it.

175
00:18:11,014 --> 00:18:13,278
梦见你真的给他找了份工作
I dreamed that you did find him a job,

176
00:18:13,350 --> 00:18:16,080
可是他疯了 还把我们一起杀了
but he'd lost his mind and killed us both.

177
00:18:16,453 --> 00:18:18,387
啊? 你和我?
- Who? - You and me!

178
00:18:19,489 --> 00:18:21,354
在那里呢?
Know where we were?

179
00:18:22,559 --> 00:18:25,551
就是在我给你买领带的地方
In that little street, Via della Croce, where I bought you

180
00:18:25,595 --> 00:18:28,564
你老婆也给你买过一条的， 还记得么?
the same tie your wife did. Do you remember?

181
00:18:28,598 --> 00:18:32,932
我真想知道 你戴的是谁给你买的
And I never knew if you were wearing hers or mine.

182
00:18:33,170 --> 00:18:37,607
梦里我们躺在床上， 相互依偎着，一丝不挂的
We were there on a cot, in each other's arms, naked.

183
00:18:38,508 --> 00:18:41,875
然后他进来把我俩都杀了
And he came in and he killed us both with a broom!

184
00:18:46,883 --> 00:18:49,909
把窗帘放下 对
- Draw the blinds more. - Yes.

185
00:18:50,353 --> 00:18:54,380
可以了.现在去走廊散散步吧
That's it. Now go into the corridor for a minute,

186
00:18:55,025 --> 00:18:57,084
然后假装你走错房间了
then pretend you've come to the wrong room

187
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,593
看到一个陌生人
and found a stranger.

188
00:18:59,029 --> 00:19:00,997
哦!就是这样 我们从没这样过
Oh, that's good. We've never done this one.

189
00:19:01,164 --> 00:19:02,825
站在那别动 让我再看看你
Hold it there. Let me look at you.

190
00:19:03,967 --> 00:19:06,868
不，不是这样，你需要再补补的桩，再多一点
No. No. Your make-up needs to be more, more...

191
00:19:10,473 --> 00:19:13,033
多点什么? 像个荡妇一样!
- More what? - More like a slut!

192
00:19:14,978 --> 00:19:17,105
来我帮你画画
Give me your eyeliner.

193
00:19:22,652 --> 00:19:24,517
这眼影不错 对，就要这样
- Nice lampshade. - Yes, yes.

194
00:19:24,588 --> 00:19:26,579
这灯好漂亮，我也想要一个放在我家 别动
- I'd like one for my place. - Don't move.

195
00:19:27,057 --> 00:19:28,354
这酒店叫什么来着?
What is this hotel called?

196
00:19:28,592 --> 00:19:29,820
旅行宾馆
The Railway Hotel.

197
00:19:30,060 --> 00:19:32,324
我要写信给我丈夫
I want to write to my husband so he'll send me

198
00:19:32,362 --> 00:19:34,796
让他马上给我快递. 他写的信很得体的
an express letter right away. He writes such nice letters.

199
00:19:35,031 --> 00:19:37,465
我会让你看看的 好，别动
I'll let you read them. - Fine, but keep still...

200
00:19:38,401 --> 00:19:39,834
做个诱惑的表情
Make a slutty face.

201
00:19:42,839 --> 00:19:44,534
走到走廊那
Go out in the corridor.

202
00:19:44,608 --> 00:19:47,008
这就是我需要演的那部分么 是的
- So, it's a part I have to play. - Yes.

203
00:19:47,043 --> 00:19:49,637
你怎么看我? 你的演员么?
Who do you think I am? One of your actresses?

204
00:19:49,746 --> 00:19:51,941
你不觉得我可以变成他们一样么
You don't think I could be one of them?

205
00:19:52,382 --> 00:19:55,283
那可不是我想要的生活
Not me. I wouldn't want to lead that life.

206
00:19:55,886 --> 00:19:57,319
我喜欢一直在家待着
I like staying home.

207
00:19:58,121 --> 00:19:59,884
好，快出去吧.我要假装睡觉了
Go on, get out. I'm sleeping now.

208
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:06,588
告诉我.你是不是很喜欢我这样呀
Tell me. If I were really to do something like this,

209
00:20:06,663 --> 00:20:07,857
你有点嫉妒了吧
would you be jealous?

210
00:20:08,598 --> 00:20:11,032
为什么?真的么?
Why? Would you really?

211
00:20:12,769 --> 00:20:14,100
也许吧
Who knows?

212
00:20:16,306 --> 00:20:19,434
你需要点什么 不，我只是走错房间了
- May I get you something? - No, I just came out on a whim.

213
00:20:19,476 --> 00:20:22,070
要我给你放点水洗澡么 不用了，我只是...
- Would you like me to run you a bath? - No, I was just...

214
00:20:22,145 --> 00:20:25,171
要喝点水么? 不了，谢谢你
- A glass of water, perhaps? - No, thank you.

215
00:20:27,617 --> 00:20:29,517
碰到谁了? 说什么呢?
What did she want? What did she say?

216
00:20:29,552 --> 00:20:33,488
是主人，她要给我杯水
The owner, she wanted to give me a glass of water.

217
00:20:33,523 --> 00:20:36,754
过来点，来
Come here. Come.

218
00:20:39,095 --> 00:20:40,494
拿开床单
Open up the sheet.

219
00:20:42,098 --> 00:20:46,558
贵度，你喜欢我么? 当然了
- Guido, do you love me a little? - Yes, yes.

220
00:21:15,198 --> 00:21:16,688
是你么，妈妈?
Is that you, Mama?

221
00:21:19,436 --> 00:21:22,166
好难过，儿子，好伤心
So many tears, my son, so many tears.

222
00:21:22,238 --> 00:21:24,035
爸爸，等等!别走
Papa, wait! Don't go.

223
00:21:25,241 --> 00:21:27,402
我们还没谈完啊
We talked so little.

224
00:21:30,580 --> 00:21:34,016
爸爸，我有好多事不明白
Listen Papa, I have so many questions.

225
00:21:37,420 --> 00:21:39,650
我还不能马上回答你
I cannot answer them yet.

226
00:21:40,657 --> 00:21:43,353
这的屋顶好低，你看看
See the ceiling here? It's so low.

227
00:21:43,793 --> 00:21:47,786
我想要个高点的 这个太糟了，儿子，我不喜欢
I would have liked it higher. It's ugly, my son, ugly.

228
00:21:48,365 --> 00:21:53,098
我想换一换了 你能帮我么?
I would have liked it different. Couldn't you take care of it?

229
00:21:53,703 --> 00:21:56,228
你画画不错，能不能帮我...
You used to draw so well. I'd like...

230
00:21:56,706 --> 00:22:00,335
哦，卡门多，本不该麻烦他的
Oh, the Commendatore, he shouldn't have bothered.

231
00:22:04,547 --> 00:22:08,677
嗨 我现在有点时间
- Hello. - Respects. He's got very little time.

232
00:22:10,420 --> 00:22:11,512
嗨
Hi.

233
00:22:11,921 --> 00:22:14,685
我的儿子怎么样了?
How is he doing, this son of mine?

234
00:22:15,358 --> 00:22:18,452
小心啊，不要让他骗了你
Careful. Don't let him move you.

235
00:22:20,263 --> 00:22:23,391
他不是很好?怎么了?
He isn't doing well? How come?

236
00:22:23,533 --> 00:22:27,003
我知道这很难过，不应该犯这样的错的
It is so hard, realizing that one has made such huge mistakes.

237
00:22:27,003 --> 00:22:27,867
可是我...
But l...

238
00:22:33,410 --> 00:22:36,573
你妈妈给你做了点心
Mother prepared you a little something.

239
00:22:37,080 --> 00:22:39,048
奶酪和桃子
A little cheese and two peaches.

240
00:22:39,783 --> 00:22:41,808
不用担心我了
Don't worry about me.

241
00:22:42,052 --> 00:22:44,350
好吧，虽然这里有点冷清
Sure, this place gets a little lonely,

242
00:22:44,421 --> 00:22:46,389
你妈妈会每天来陪我的
but your mother comes every day.

243
00:22:46,956 --> 00:22:51,086
她给我做伴 帮我打点一切
She keeps me company, you know. And keeps everything in order.

244
00:22:51,461 --> 00:22:53,326
应该客气点的
A little decorum is always necessary.

245
00:22:53,596 --> 00:22:55,427
我们就是这么长大的
That's how we were brought up.

246
00:22:55,665 --> 00:22:57,758
和你妻子，陆纱也是这样的么?
And with your wife, Luisa -- all fine?

247
00:22:57,801 --> 00:22:59,200
是啊，陆纱
Yes. Luisa...

248
00:22:59,335 --> 00:23:02,634
你们俩在一起真好. 再见了，我的儿子
You two together have been my joy. Goodbye, son...

249
00:23:07,977 --> 00:23:11,504
这是什么地方? 你喜欢吗?
What is this place? Do you like it here?

250
00:23:12,615 --> 00:23:15,049
我还没布置好呢
I haven't figured it out yet.

251
00:23:15,885 --> 00:23:20,049
这里会变得很温馨的
But it's going much better.

252
00:23:21,091 --> 00:23:25,528
首先，看这...
At first, you see, at first...

253
00:23:28,398 --> 00:23:32,562
贵度! 我的宝贝儿子 让我看看你还需要点什么?
Guido! I do my best. What more can I do?

254
00:23:43,480 --> 00:23:46,210
可怜的贵度，你肯定精疲力尽了 要不咱们回家吧
Poor Guido, you must be tired. Shall we go home?

255
00:23:48,184 --> 00:23:50,744
我是陆纱，你的老婆啊 不记得我了么?
I'm Luisa, your wife. Don't you recognize me?

256
00:23:50,787 --> 00:23:51,947
你想什么呢?
What are you thinking about?

257
00:24:25,121 --> 00:24:26,588
嗨! 你好!!
- Hello. - Hello.

258
00:24:44,140 --> 00:24:45,072
下午好!
Good afternoon.

259
00:25:13,503 --> 00:25:16,233
贵度!过两天， 你就会适应的
Guido! In a few days, I'll get you an introduction

260
00:25:16,306 --> 00:25:18,797
很快你就可以得到建议了
so you can get all the advice you need.

261
00:25:19,108 --> 00:25:20,507
很奥妙的雕塑吧
Nice mystical figure. Right?

262
00:25:20,977 --> 00:25:22,968
我做了三个老人
I brought you the three old men.

263
00:25:23,046 --> 00:25:25,037
一个俄国人 还有一个退役的将军
One is a Russian, another is a retired general...

264
00:25:25,114 --> 00:25:26,206
那个老人?
What old men?

265
00:25:26,282 --> 00:25:27,874
就是演父亲的那个啊
The ones for the role of the Father.

266
00:25:27,951 --> 00:25:30,078
挡着我，瑟萨芮诺
Cover me, Cesarino...

267
00:25:32,655 --> 00:25:34,316
往那跑呢. 布冯
Come here, buffoon.

268
00:25:34,857 --> 00:25:38,520
你好吗? 看到你太好了，我的老朋友
How are you? So nice to see you, Super Tarzan!

269
00:25:38,962 --> 00:25:41,192
我叫了你6遍了 哦，我知道了
- I called you six times. - Yes, yes I know.

270
00:25:41,264 --> 00:25:43,391
珂劳迪亚的剧本怎样了 嗯?
- It's about Claudia's script. - So?

271
00:25:43,900 --> 00:25:45,128
我本想寄过去给你的
I thought about mailing it to you.

272
00:25:45,201 --> 00:25:47,192
其实我已经寄出去了 是么?
In fact, I've already mailed it. - Really?

273
00:25:47,403 --> 00:25:50,304
你看起来还不错 怎么不回去继续演戏?
You've still got your looks. Why don't you go back to acting?

274
00:25:50,373 --> 00:25:52,773
我整晚都在设想关于宇宙飞船的剧本
I was up all night with an idea for the spaceship.

275
00:25:52,842 --> 00:25:54,434
我们一起来研究一下如何
Why don't we make the upper story...

276
00:25:54,510 --> 00:25:58,276
别碰我的胳膊，我不喜欢这样，穿上夹克
Conocchia, don't take my arm! I hate it! And wear a jacket!

277
00:25:59,282 --> 00:26:01,375
和你说话还要穿衣服...
Now I need to wear a jacket to talk to you...

278
00:26:01,517 --> 00:26:03,508
你好啊，旅途如何?
How are you? How was your trip?

279
00:26:03,586 --> 00:26:05,554
很好，有一个小时了
Good. It's been an hour...

280
00:26:07,123 --> 00:26:11,150
好炫目的布景，太美了
What a blinding vision! Beautiful!

281
00:26:14,063 --> 00:26:15,792
是么? 嗯
- Really? - Yes.

282
00:26:16,199 --> 00:26:18,133
你总是夸奖我
You're always telling me I'm 'bellissima'

283
00:26:18,201 --> 00:26:20,431
但是还没说过关于我的戏
but you never tell me about my part.

284
00:26:20,837 --> 00:26:24,398
拍出来效果如何? 当然好了，所以还是让你继续演
How was my screen test? - Great, or you wouldn't be here.

285
00:26:24,641 --> 00:26:30,705
他们说我该更丰满些，多吃点通心粉
They told me I have to look motherly and eat a lot of pasta.

286
00:26:33,182 --> 00:26:35,173
再胖点，是这样么?
I should gain six pounds. Is this all?

287
00:26:35,351 --> 00:26:37,444
看看，你知道的都比我多了
See? You already know more than I do.

288
00:26:38,454 --> 00:26:41,048
你是作者，你该知道的比我多阿
You are the author. You should be telling me something.

289
00:26:42,158 --> 00:26:44,285
这位女士该如何呢? 什么?
- What should this lady do? - What?

290
00:26:45,428 --> 00:26:46,588
阿哥思尼!
Agostini!

291
00:26:48,364 --> 00:26:51,561
打扰一下 酒店已经可以了
I don't want to bother you. The hotel is grand,

292
00:26:51,634 --> 00:26:54,797
威士忌，太好了 我还有3个问题
the whisky, excellent. But I have three questions.

293
00:26:54,871 --> 00:26:58,637
好好，等一下 啊，什么?
Yes, yes, later. What is it? Ah, yes, yes. Pardon me.

294
00:26:59,175 --> 00:27:00,574
阿哥思尼，我们应该...
Agostini, we should...

295
00:27:00,643 --> 00:27:03,134
我不太想和他谈
I just didn't feel like talking to that guy.

296
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:06,244
珂劳迪亚全世界都有档期
Claudia is getting offers from all over the world.

297
00:27:06,616 --> 00:27:09,449
我可不想让她一直等 给她点什么
I can't keep her waiting. Give her something.

298
00:27:09,619 --> 00:27:12,645
你有剧本么 随便什么，或者什么设想
Do you have a script, a few pages, an idea?

299
00:27:12,722 --> 00:27:15,657
珂劳迪亚知道这主意不错吧
Does Claudia realize that this might be a great part?

300
00:27:15,692 --> 00:27:18,923
这个角色她最合适 我跟她解释一下
Perhaps the best she's ever played? I'll explain...

301
00:27:27,470 --> 00:27:29,461
我从一个朋友的角度说，你会失去她的
I'm telling you as a friend, you're gonna lose her.

302
00:27:29,505 --> 00:27:32,235
你想看看老人么? 你怎么了?我们已经准备...
- You want to see the old men or not? - Are you crazy? We're ready...

303
00:27:32,575 --> 00:27:34,042
什么? 老人啊
What? - The old men.

304
00:27:34,110 --> 00:27:35,236
在那里? 这啊
- Where are they? - Here.

305
00:27:36,012 --> 00:27:39,140
斯格诺拉打电话来，说不想住那个酒店了
Signora Carla called. She doesn't want to stay in that hotel.

306
00:27:39,215 --> 00:27:41,581
很恶心.她是对的 我该怎么办?带她过来?
It's ugly. She's right. - What can I do? Bring her here?

307
00:27:42,552 --> 00:27:44,247
我会去叫老人过来
I'll call the old men.

308
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:46,515
我想给你介绍一下我妻子
Sorry, I wanted to introduce you to my little wife.

309
00:27:47,557 --> 00:27:50,424
见到你好激动啊!
Thrilled.

310
00:27:50,927 --> 00:27:54,954
她有时候也写作的.是个女性杂志的专栏作家
She writes too. She's a columnist for some ladies' magazines.

311
00:27:55,031 --> 00:27:57,795
她有点问题想讨教一下
She's got a few questions for you.

312
00:27:57,867 --> 00:28:01,359
我的读者们疯狂的追求浪漫
My readers go crazy for romance.

313
00:28:01,771 --> 00:28:05,730
跟我说说你的浪漫史吧
Could you tell me something about your love life?

314
00:28:05,808 --> 00:28:08,174
他们在这呢! 跟多特里打个招呼吧
Here they are. Say hello to the Dottore.

315
00:28:08,611 --> 00:28:12,707
坐下，将军你也坐下
Step down. You too, General.

316
00:28:14,717 --> 00:28:16,412
您的年龄?
- How old are you? - 70.

317
00:28:16,486 --> 00:28:18,215
您呢?
- And you? - 64.

318
00:28:19,756 --> 00:28:21,587
您?
- And you? - 68.

319
00:28:25,361 --> 00:28:27,192
他们还不够老啊
They aren't old enough.

320
00:28:27,263 --> 00:28:29,026
还不够?这家伙可都快不行的人了啊
What? This one has one foot in the grave.

321
00:28:29,065 --> 00:28:31,363
下次我会带来三个特别的 您要得那种悲剧型的
Next time I'll get three corpses. You asked for a pathetic type...

322
00:28:31,401 --> 00:28:35,269
保证让你一看就想哭的那种
This one makes you wanna cry the minute you see him.

323
00:28:40,777 --> 00:28:42,142
你好，卡门多
Hello, Commendatore.

324
00:28:45,848 --> 00:28:48,408
你跪下后，我该怎么办?
If you kneel, what do I do?

325
00:28:48,484 --> 00:28:50,008
快起来，别伤了你自己 你好吗?小贵度
Get up or you'll hurt yourself. How are you, little Guido?

326
00:28:52,722 --> 00:28:54,417
你好，卡门多
Hello, Commendatore.

327
00:28:54,490 --> 00:28:56,720
我们做直升机来的，吵死了
We took a helicopter. This one screamed the whole way.

328
00:28:56,793 --> 00:28:57,555
游泳池在那里?
Where's the swimming pool?

329
00:28:57,627 --> 00:28:59,492
我们还没入住呢，别吵
We haven't even checked in. Shut up!

330
00:28:59,862 --> 00:29:01,022
怎么样，治疗有效么? 有的
Has the treatment helped? - Yes.

331
00:29:01,164 --> 00:29:02,290
这里感觉好点了么? 这是什么?
- Feeling better? Here. - What is it?

332
00:29:02,432 --> 00:29:03,490
纪念币
Just a token.

333
00:29:03,633 --> 00:29:05,396
你总是带礼物来
- You're always giving me presents. - It's just like mine.

334
00:29:05,535 --> 00:29:06,729
干吗包起来呢
It doesn't need winding.

335
00:29:06,869 --> 00:29:08,734
是块表，一块表，快来看
A watch! A little watch, everyone!

336
00:29:12,008 --> 00:29:15,876
那么，你的思路该清晰些了吧 是啊，我觉得是
- So, are your ideas any clearer now? - Yes, I really think so.

337
00:29:16,479 --> 00:29:18,413
我们找到美国人了...
We've got the Americans...

338
00:29:46,642 --> 00:29:49,611
我见过她的证件，已经52岁了
I've seen her passport. She's 52 years old?

339
00:29:49,679 --> 00:29:51,613
哦，还不是很老嘛
Ah, she's a little girl.

340
00:29:52,114 --> 00:29:53,240
晚上好，西诺拉
Good evening, signora.

341
00:29:53,983 --> 00:29:56,781
这是谁啊，亲爱的
And who are you, darling?

342
00:31:02,518 --> 00:31:06,010
导演先生，我还有个小问题
Mr. Director, another little question...

343
00:31:12,228 --> 00:31:15,527
他想知道天主教和马克思之主义之间的联系
He wants to know the relationship between Catholicism and Marxism.

344
00:31:15,565 --> 00:31:16,896
谢谢你，我知道了
Thank you, I got it.

345
00:31:17,166 --> 00:31:19,657
你想知道我的政治倾向
You want to know about my political affiliation.

346
00:31:19,902 --> 00:31:24,100
作为一个诚实的人，所有象我这样的意大利人
As an honest man, and all of you ltalians are,

347
00:31:24,173 --> 00:31:27,165
都可以回答你的问题
you should be able to answer me.

348
00:31:27,243 --> 00:31:31,475
意大利人天生就都信仰天主教么?
Is ltaly an essentially Catholic country?

349
00:31:31,514 --> 00:31:32,208
是啊，就是这样的
Yes, it is!

350
00:31:32,248 --> 00:31:34,216
吃你的冰激凌，别多嘴
You shut up and eat your ice-cream.

351
00:31:34,717 --> 00:31:37,550
这是飞船的初步构想
It's the estimate for the spaceship.

352
00:31:39,221 --> 00:31:42,520
我等会儿好好和你谈谈，面对面的
I need to talk to you later, face to face,

353
00:31:42,592 --> 00:31:46,892
我一点思绪也没有了 感觉一点也不好
I'm at the end of my rope. This is a madhouse!

354
00:31:46,963 --> 00:31:50,330
那我们还是以后再谈好了 你的胆库醇还高么?
Fine, we'll discuss it later. What was that about your cholesterol?

355
00:32:11,554 --> 00:32:15,046
一个伟大的作家. 菲茨杰拉德（英国小说家）
...only one great writer. The early Fitzgerald.

356
00:32:15,124 --> 00:32:19,288
后来他的作品变得豪放，有些兽性的现实主义
Then his writing became an orgy of pragmatism or brutal realism.

357
00:32:19,762 --> 00:32:23,027
呵呵，比较矛盾的问题
What does Left or Right mean?

358
00:32:23,099 --> 00:32:25,966
你这么个乐天派居然相信这些
You're such an optimist to believe that in a world

359
00:32:26,035 --> 00:32:28,833
在这混沌的世界，也有人自认清高的
this confused and chaotic there are people so lucid

360
00:32:28,904 --> 00:32:32,067
这些都是矛盾的象征
as to belong exclusively to the Left or the Right.

361
00:32:32,108 --> 00:32:36,272
这就是美国人的思维
The Americans have this new theory about cholesterol...

362
00:32:36,412 --> 00:32:39,347
你的冰淇淋还不错吧 嗯，好吃
- Is your ice-cream good? - Very good.

363
00:32:43,719 --> 00:32:46,449
能不能明确告诉我，她有多少出戏可演
Could you say approximately how many scenes she'll be in?

364
00:32:46,589 --> 00:32:47,523
什么?
What?

365
00:32:47,523 --> 00:32:49,718
戏么? 5场
- How many scenes? - Five.

366
00:32:52,228 --> 00:32:53,388
只有5场么?
Only five.

367
00:32:53,596 --> 00:32:56,121
或许6，7个
Maybe six, or even seven.

368
00:32:56,766 --> 00:32:57,858
晚上好
Good evening.

369
00:32:58,634 --> 00:32:59,794
Hi，贵度
Hi, Guido.

370
00:33:01,003 --> 00:33:03,301
大使在看夫人呢
The Ambassador's got his eye on signora.

371
00:33:08,844 --> 00:33:09,833
怎么了?
So?

372
00:33:09,912 --> 00:33:11,812
我想您应该知道这些 好的，我已经知道了
- I thought you'd want to know. - Good, now I know.

373
00:33:12,081 --> 00:33:14,675
我帮您约她跳舞怎样? 去问问她吧
- Do you want me to ask her to dance? - Yes, ask her.

374
00:33:15,317 --> 00:33:17,547
亲爱的朋友们，事实是...
Dear friends there's only one truth...

375
00:33:17,987 --> 00:33:22,856
我是多么渴望知道，我得角色是什么
But I am so anxious to know, to understand my character.

376
00:33:22,925 --> 00:33:26,520
电影开始前，我需要酝酿一下角色
I need to coexist with my character for a while before shooting...

377
00:33:26,595 --> 00:33:29,723
夫人说想知道她能演什么
The lady says she needs to know her character.

378
00:33:32,668 --> 00:33:36,798
我要加深对她的了解 她的想法，要不我会演不好的
I need to get inside her skin, her ideas, or I'll fail.

379
00:33:37,239 --> 00:33:39,707
作家还没根您解释你的角色么?
Hasn't the Maestro explained the part yet?

380
00:33:39,775 --> 00:33:42,369
还没呢 真抱歉，亲爱的女士
- No. - I am sorry, dear lady.

381
00:33:42,445 --> 00:33:46,074
我还不知道那么多 我只是个制作人
I don't have such information. I'm only the producer.

382
00:33:46,415 --> 00:33:50,283
贵度，你知道我的 对，您并不了解电影那些事
Guido, isn't it true that I know nothing? - Right. Not a thing.

383
00:33:58,561 --> 00:34:00,358
可以休息3天了
And now three days of rest.

384
00:34:03,566 --> 00:34:08,401
春天的樱桃，过来我们一起享受一下这春色
They look like glass. The first cherries of spring.

385
00:34:12,775 --> 00:34:13,935
祝贺贵度么
Thanks. And for Guido?

386
00:34:21,884 --> 00:34:23,875
马里奥，好好祝贺他
Mario Mezzabotta, all 200 pounds of him.

387
00:34:25,254 --> 00:34:26,846
我们散散步如何?
Shall we take a little walk?

388
00:34:31,060 --> 00:34:37,556
我知道...你认为我注定失败
I know... Naturally, you think I've lost it.

389
00:34:37,633 --> 00:34:38,463
嗯
Yes.

390
00:34:38,601 --> 00:34:41,695
我比她大30岁，可这不是问题.
- I'm 30 years her senior. So what? - It's all right.

391
00:34:41,737 --> 00:34:46,071
我也许有点愚蠢，老的有点笨了 在她身上花费点，没什么
I may be the fool, the old imbecile, the one who foots the bill. So what?

392
00:34:47,243 --> 00:34:53,649
能不能说点建设性的意见
Could you create something important, beautiful and real on a commission?

393
00:34:53,649 --> 00:34:55,674
比如，就当教皇让你这么做
For instance, if the Pope asked you?

394
00:34:56,418 --> 00:34:58,682
好吧，好吧，我会考虑的 失陪一下
Yes, yes. I'll think about it. Excuse me.

395
00:35:01,123 --> 00:35:03,216
听着，我并不怀疑自己
Listen, I'm not deluding myself.

396
00:35:03,692 --> 00:35:06,752
她可能只是为了钱和我在一起的
Maybe she's only with me for the money.

397
00:35:07,763 --> 00:35:09,253
事实上就是这样的
Actually, that's certainly it.

398
00:35:09,431 --> 00:35:12,059
可我从来没这么爱过一个人
But I've never felt closer to anybody in my life.

399
00:35:13,435 --> 00:35:17,269
看看她，美貌，迷人，又那么惹人疼爱
Just look at her. She's pretty, charming, intelligent.

400
00:35:17,640 --> 00:35:19,767
她是女人中的女人.难道只是钱这么简单?
She has it all. Only for the money?

401
00:35:20,276 --> 00:35:23,404
现在有钱的年轻人很多啊
But there are so many rich young men around these days, loads of them.

402
00:35:23,479 --> 00:35:24,741
很明显，她很在乎你
It's clear. She cares for you.

403
00:35:25,281 --> 00:35:29,411
事实上，她从未让我觉得不舒服
Right. And she hasn't tried to pressure me.

404
00:35:29,785 --> 00:35:31,946
我可是个理性的人
I made up my mind rationally.

405
00:35:32,588 --> 00:35:35,557
她也从未要求取代我妻子
The poor thing has never even mentioned my wife,

406
00:35:35,624 --> 00:35:37,888
我的家庭，一点怨言都没有
my family, never a reproach.

407
00:35:38,160 --> 00:35:39,525
你们怎么认识的?
How did you meet her?

408
00:35:41,363 --> 00:35:44,457
在伦敦，她和我女儿读一个学校的
In London. She was in school with my daughter.

409
00:35:45,668 --> 00:35:47,192
您结婚了多久了?
How many years have you been married?

410
00:35:47,269 --> 00:35:49,100
很久了，有31年了
Many. 31.

411
00:35:49,438 --> 00:35:50,803
聊聊你的妻子...
And your wife...

412
00:35:51,507 --> 00:35:54,305
我老婆一点都不喜欢她，对她很凶
My wife took it really badly. She hates her.

413
00:35:55,244 --> 00:35:58,407
格洛里亚，这种事总是要露馅的
While Gloria, poor thing, is fond of her.

414
00:36:00,616 --> 00:36:03,016
你是不是认为我很蠢
So spell it out. I am a fool!

415
00:36:03,385 --> 00:36:05,853
我们定下档期吧，什么日子
There must be a shooting schedule. Dates.

416
00:36:05,921 --> 00:36:09,084
我们可以不用德国人的 还有其他选择
Otherwise we're off to Germany. We have other offers.

417
00:36:09,658 --> 00:36:12,252
你会支持我到最后么?
Will you be leaving me in the dark 'til the end?

418
00:36:16,632 --> 00:36:18,725
你看起来一点也不自信
You look like a little snail.

419
00:36:19,068 --> 00:36:21,468
那里不自信了?
- What is a little snail? - Une petite escargot.

420
00:36:27,776 --> 00:36:30,142
我已经看到希望了
Can you hear the voice of the springs?

421
00:36:33,115 --> 00:36:35,743
罗马人说这是“希望之泉”
The Romans used to call it 'Happy Waters.'

422
00:36:49,198 --> 00:36:52,861
玛雅，我们来吧
Maya, let's entertain these bores.

423
00:36:53,769 --> 00:36:55,566
可以嘛?
May l?

424
00:36:57,973 --> 00:37:00,908
准备好了么，玛雅? 我拿的是什么啊
Are you ready, Maya? What am I holding?

425
00:37:02,177 --> 00:37:04,042
有绒毛的钱包啊
A velvet purse.

426
00:37:04,313 --> 00:37:06,838
我说的是里面 一个白色手帕
- And inside? - A white handkerchief.

427
00:37:08,017 --> 00:37:09,712
红的吧
A red one.

428
00:37:11,020 --> 00:37:13,488
没有药吧 哦不，没有药的
- No drugs, I hope. - No, it's aspirin.

429
00:37:14,957 --> 00:37:17,255
一个钱包 里面有钱嘛?
- A purse. - Is there any money in it?

430
00:37:17,526 --> 00:37:20,495
2，725 里拉
2,725 lire.

431
00:37:23,899 --> 00:37:26,026
这位女士在想什么呢?
And this lady here. What is she thinking?

432
00:37:26,368 --> 00:37:28,165
我希望她可别想歪了
No dirty thoughts, I hope.

433
00:37:28,237 --> 00:37:29,670
也许真的在想事呢
Just think about something.

434
00:37:29,738 --> 00:37:30,966
那在想什么呢?
About what?

435
00:37:31,040 --> 00:37:32,507
也许是讨你喜欢呢 你在想么
Whatever you like. Are you thinking?

436
00:37:33,976 --> 00:37:34,704
是啊
Yes.

437
00:37:34,843 --> 00:37:38,244
我真想再多活上100年
I'd like to live another 1 00 years.

438
00:37:40,549 --> 00:37:41,914
祝你好运
Best of luck!

439
00:37:43,352 --> 00:37:46,913
这位漂亮的女士戴的是什么?
And what is in this pretty lady's head?

440
00:37:46,989 --> 00:37:48,320
我说是
Let me be.

441
00:37:48,791 --> 00:37:50,622
我想起一个人么
May I think about someone?

442
00:37:50,693 --> 00:37:52,388
说吧，小姐
Yes. Go ahead, Lady!

443
00:37:52,761 --> 00:37:56,197
我不好意思说
Forget about it. I'm ashamed.

444
00:37:56,265 --> 00:37:57,960
为什么?
What about?

445
00:37:58,167 --> 00:37:59,725
我真的想起一个人
Can I really think of a person?

446
00:37:59,802 --> 00:38:02,430
我不想让你知道
I'd be afraid to have my thoughts read.

447
00:38:02,504 --> 00:38:04,472
别怕，亲爱的 告诉我没什么的
Don't you worry darling, no risk there.

448
00:38:04,540 --> 00:38:06,337
我们还是走吧 有点冷了
Would you like to leave? It's cold.

449
00:38:06,408 --> 00:38:09,639
亲一下换一个耳光 对么?
A little kiss and a big slap. Is that right?

450
00:38:12,114 --> 00:38:15,572
亲爱的女士们先生们， 你们一定在想，“这个骗子”
Ladies and gentlemen, you're thinking, 'What a trickster.'

451
00:38:15,651 --> 00:38:18,313
对不起，其实这里并没有什么玄机
Well, sorry to disappoint you, but there's no trick.

452
00:38:18,387 --> 00:38:21,550
这只是个巧合而已
And it isn't just a coincidence.

453
00:38:21,623 --> 00:38:24,057
同时也证明了异性并不一定相吸
It's an exceptional example of magnetic fields and telepathy.

454
00:38:24,126 --> 00:38:27,391
我这就是我要告诉玛雅小姐的
I transmit your thoughts to Mlle. Maya.

455
00:38:27,830 --> 00:38:30,958
你，真的认为可以骗过我们?
You! Do you believe you can hide your thoughts?

456
00:38:39,908 --> 00:38:43,139
请离她远点 别再坚持了
Please, leave her alone. Don't insist.

457
00:38:43,879 --> 00:38:45,210
有些想法很奇怪的
Thoughts are sacred.

458
00:38:46,015 --> 00:38:48,006
其实这只是个游戏而已
See, it's all a game.

459
00:38:48,150 --> 00:38:49,276
玛雅，你准备好了么?
Maya, are you ready?

460
00:38:50,519 --> 00:38:54,853
等一下，请告诉我先生们在想什么
Just a moment, could we know what you gentlemen are thinking?

461
00:38:55,090 --> 00:38:56,182
那么就问问您吧
You for instance.

462
00:38:56,258 --> 00:38:57,657
您在想什么?
What are you thinking?

463
00:38:57,726 --> 00:38:59,694
还有什么?我的大导演.
What else? My director. My cross and my delight.

464
00:39:01,330 --> 00:39:03,298
你好吗? 不错，你呢
- How are you? - Fine. And you?

465
00:39:04,500 --> 00:39:05,899
有些日子没见到你了...好几年拉!
It has been quite a while... years!

466
00:39:05,968 --> 00:39:07,993
哦，真是，天啊
Unfortunately yes, my dear.

467
00:39:08,604 --> 00:39:11,368
等等，你现在很出名了嘛
Just a moment. You're famous now.

468
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:16,537
少来了 快点告诉我这里面有什么名堂
Cut it out. Just tell me what's your trick?

469
00:39:16,612 --> 00:39:19,172
嗯，半真半假吧
Well, it's partly a trick, but part of it is real.

470
00:39:19,248 --> 00:39:22,081
我并不完全明白，但就是象这样的 能变成别的什么么?
I don't know how, but it happens. - Can you transmit anything?

471
00:39:22,151 --> 00:39:24,676
什么都行，除非她失手
Anything. Except for her to get lost.

472
00:39:25,554 --> 00:39:27,317
想试试看么? 好啊，等等
- Do you want to try? - Yes. Wait.

473
00:39:27,823 --> 00:39:29,586
我跟你打赌，这肯定行的
I bet now, with you, it won't work.

474
00:39:34,997 --> 00:39:39,900
我不太明白.可以再来一次...
I don't understand. I can't repeat...

475
00:40:05,894 --> 00:40:10,058
阿撒...尼撒...摩挲? 是这样嘛?
Asa... nisi... masa? Is this right?

476
00:40:11,233 --> 00:40:13,292
对的? 就是这样
- Right? - Yes.

477
00:40:13,635 --> 00:40:15,694
那究竟什么意思呢?
But what does it mean?

478
00:40:22,277 --> 00:40:24,211
贵度，过来这 你在那呢?
Guido, come here! Where are you?

479
00:40:25,214 --> 00:40:26,977
别被宠坏了哦!太奇妙了
Don't be spoiled! What a wonder!

480
00:40:27,049 --> 00:40:28,380
我还不想洗澡，真的不想...
I don't want to take a bath, I don't want to...

481
00:40:28,450 --> 00:40:29,940
是你过来...还是让我去抓你?
Come here... Iet me catch you?

482
00:40:30,119 --> 00:40:31,416
我知道这流氓想干什么
I know what that rascal wants.

483
00:40:31,487 --> 00:40:33,079
他想她的宝贝背着他吧
He wants to be carried by his sweetheart,

484
00:40:33,155 --> 00:40:34,747
是他吧，那个猛男
doesn't he, the strapping lad.

485
00:40:34,823 --> 00:40:37,792
来，过来
Come here. Come here.

486
00:40:37,860 --> 00:40:40,192
他从来不想洗药浴，淘气的孩子
He never wants to take the wine bath, the naughty boy.

487
00:40:40,262 --> 00:40:42,890
难道你不想治好，将来变成真正的男人么?
Don't you know that if you do you'll grow into a strong man?

488
00:40:42,965 --> 00:40:46,059
贵度 是胆小鬼，贵度 是胆小鬼
Guido is scared! Guido is scared!

489
00:40:57,713 --> 00:41:00,011
恶棍是要被诅咒的
The Devil and damnation!

490
00:41:08,123 --> 00:41:09,750
奶奶，奶奶
Granny, granny!

491
00:41:09,825 --> 00:41:11,554
今年的木头都受潮了
The wood is all wet this year.

492
00:41:11,627 --> 00:41:13,424
这猫每天四处乱窜，跟你爷爷一个样
This prowling cat is just like your grandfather.

493
00:41:13,495 --> 00:41:15,963
整天乱跑，只有吃饭的时候才回来
Always on the prowl and only comes in for food.

494
00:41:17,099 --> 00:41:19,294
真可耻，快睡觉吧!
Shame on you! Go to bed.

495
00:41:20,536 --> 00:41:23,767
上次我就让他吃了闭门羹
Last time I slammed the door in his face

496
00:41:23,839 --> 00:41:25,966
整整两天不让他回来
and left him outside for two days.

497
00:41:27,075 --> 00:41:32,069
嫁给他真实委屈我了!
I could have married again and found a handsome man,

498
00:41:32,681 --> 00:41:35,206
我的条件完全可以找个比他更好的
rest assured, better than your grandfather.

499
00:41:35,651 --> 00:41:37,710
我当年真是太笨了
What an idiot I am!

500
00:41:38,787 --> 00:41:42,518
要是我选了第一个丈夫的话，无论在天堂
I thought that if I took another husband, my first husband,

501
00:41:42,591 --> 00:41:46,493
还是在地狱，我都会比现在幸福的
whether in heaven or hell, wouldn't have waited.

502
00:41:47,462 --> 00:41:50,522
安静点，睡觉吧，你们这帮小鬼
Be quiet! Go to bed, children!

503
00:42:19,995 --> 00:42:21,986
奶奶，珂劳迪亚身上湿了
Nanny, Claudio wet himself!

504
00:42:22,064 --> 00:42:25,192
这是干什么呢?快睡觉去 你也是，快去
What are you doing? Go to sleep. You too, sleep.

505
00:42:31,740 --> 00:42:34,903
小贵度, 快进被子里去 外面冷，别乱动
Little Guido, get under the covers. It's cold. Be still.

506
00:42:40,582 --> 00:42:41,776
你祈祷了么?
Did you say your prayers?

507
00:42:44,753 --> 00:42:46,812
看你这漂亮的小卷毛，太美了
Aren't you a beautiful sticky bun? The most beautiful!

508
00:42:46,888 --> 00:42:48,685
我也要亲一下
Give me a kiss, too.

509
00:42:48,757 --> 00:42:51,726
你最喜欢的是我嘛? 对不对呀?
Who do you love best? Me? Is that right?

510
00:42:51,793 --> 00:42:53,624
你骗不了我的
You can't fool me.

511
00:42:53,695 --> 00:42:55,822
小心我打你屁股
I'm going to give you a spanking.

512
00:42:57,866 --> 00:43:03,304
你可逃不过我的眼睛的
I can tell when you're pretending.

513
00:43:06,108 --> 00:43:08,235
小鬼，好好睡
Sleep tight, little creatures.

514
00:43:08,844 --> 00:43:10,505
合上眼
Close your eyes.

515
00:43:27,262 --> 00:43:28,889
贵度，别睡了好么
Guido, don't close your eyes tonight!

516
00:43:28,930 --> 00:43:31,398
今天晚上怪怪的，你不会害怕，是吧?
It's the night the portrait's eyes move. You're not scared, are you?

517
00:43:31,466 --> 00:43:32,933
你必须要安静!
You must be quiet!

518
00:43:33,001 --> 00:43:35,663
古丝那叔叔将会窥探那个角落，并且发现那个宝藏的!
Uncle Agostino will look into the corner and find the treasure!

519
00:43:35,737 --> 00:43:37,671
别害怕!贵度!我们会有钱的!
Don't be afraid, Guido! We'll be rich!

520
00:43:37,739 --> 00:43:44,838
你记得那个咒语嘛?阿撒...尼撒摩挲... 阿撒 尼撒摩挲...嘘!!
Do you remember the spell? Asa Nisi Masa... Asa Nisi Masa... sh!

521
00:44:18,880 --> 00:44:22,839
先生，有几个从罗马打来的 电话找您，我猜是您的妻子
Sir, you got two or three calls from Rome. Your wife, I think.

522
00:44:22,918 --> 00:44:26,183
好吧，让我听吧.
Fine. Get me the line.

523
00:44:26,621 --> 00:44:28,885
基诺，让这位先生听电话. 好的.
- Gino, get the gentleman the line. - All right.

524
00:44:28,957 --> 00:44:32,916
给您!晚安，先生! 晚安!
- This is for you. Good night, sir. - Good night.

525
00:44:34,629 --> 00:44:36,722
玛赛勒，那个从罗马打来的电话?很快啊.
Marcella, that call from Rome, quickly.

526
00:44:47,676 --> 00:44:50,509
这没什么?
No, I'm not offended.

527
00:44:51,313 --> 00:44:53,178
让我不舒服的只有一件事
There's only one thing that offends me.

528
00:44:54,383 --> 00:45:01,186
你认识我.不可能
You know me. No.

529
00:45:02,190 --> 00:45:06,183
我原谅了他所有的一切.
I forgive him everything.

530
00:45:13,635 --> 00:45:16,604
我们少聊一会吧.
Let's have a little chat.

531
00:45:16,938 --> 00:45:18,530
挨着我坐一下!
Sit beside me for a moment.

532
00:45:18,673 --> 00:45:22,131
不行，我要睡觉了，我很累，并且我在等一个电话.
No, I'm going to bed. I'm very tired and waiting for a call.

533
00:45:23,945 --> 00:45:24,570
你想要点吗?
Would you like some?

534
00:45:24,646 --> 00:45:26,443
不，谢谢.我觉得头很痛!
No, thank you. I have such a headache.

535
00:45:27,649 --> 00:45:28,775
把你的手给我.
Give me your hands.

536
00:45:30,018 --> 00:45:31,417
不，还是坐下吧!
No, sit down.

537
00:45:33,455 --> 00:45:36,049
我有的左手有治疗的功效.
I have a healing fluid in my left hand.

538
00:45:36,591 --> 00:45:38,616
当我腹痛的时候，我就用它止痛.
I put it on my belly when it aches.

539
00:45:39,394 --> 00:45:40,691
脱掉你的帽子.
Take off your hat.

540
00:45:45,734 --> 00:45:46,860
好些了吗?
Is it any better?

541
00:45:51,706 --> 00:45:52,900
嗯，好一些了.
Yes, maybe.

542
00:45:57,979 --> 00:45:59,344
你为什么那样看着我?
Why do you look at me that way?

543
00:46:00,449 --> 00:46:04,613
哦，不要说我漂亮.那会让我会觉得是一种侮辱.
Oh, don't say I'm beautiful. You make it sound insulting.

544
00:46:05,153 --> 00:46:06,450
你没事吧?
What's with you?

545
00:46:08,323 --> 00:46:09,415
我不知道.
I don't know.

546
00:46:11,626 --> 00:46:18,190
我觉得我的生活和工作中 一切决定都是错误的.
I feel I made all the wrong decisions in my life and in my work.

547
00:46:22,604 --> 00:46:25,573
不要折磨我了，快说吧
Tell me, why do you enjoy torturing me?

548
00:46:25,740 --> 00:46:27,207
折磨你?
Torturing you?

549
00:46:28,343 --> 00:46:30,709
像个朋友一样的说真话吧!
Talk to me as you would to an old friend.

550
00:46:31,179 --> 00:46:34,239
我应该多了解了解导演
I need to feel close to my director.

551
00:46:40,355 --> 00:46:42,448
你看了我上一部片子么，在贝尔格莱德的那部
Did you see my last movie, the one shot in Belgrade?

552
00:46:42,891 --> 00:46:47,123
我的角色是个妇人 显的有些苍老的女人
My character was a woman marked by the injuries of time,

553
00:46:47,195 --> 00:46:50,164
但是风韵犹存
yet still desirable...

554
00:46:50,899 --> 00:46:53,732
来点 “神秘感” 虽然我并不知道那是什么
- Play "Mystification". - I don't know it.

555
00:46:54,269 --> 00:46:55,600
但是可以演...
But yes...

556
00:46:55,670 --> 00:46:57,535
太刺激了...这角色...
What a character... this woman...

557
00:46:59,374 --> 00:47:00,568
可是...
But...

558
00:47:00,609 --> 00:47:02,509
一个让人感到安逸和被爱着感觉
In whom people find protection and love.

559
00:47:04,646 --> 00:47:08,446
我就是这样一个人 生活中和她一样的
I am this character. I am like her in life and love.

560
00:47:09,551 --> 00:47:11,212
所以我感到很孤独
That's why I'm so lonely.

561
00:47:12,621 --> 00:47:15,055
我总是原谅男人所作的不对...
And I have always forgiven everything in the man...

562
00:47:15,123 --> 00:47:17,751
因为我爱他们.
the men, I love.

563
00:47:18,059 --> 00:47:20,391
先生，罗马的电话 谢谢
- Sir, Rome on the line. - Thank you.

564
00:47:20,462 --> 00:47:22,862
我很恶毒，贪欲
I am very sensual. Wicked, too!

565
00:47:22,931 --> 00:47:24,899
对，对，就是这样的感觉! 我马上就回来
Yes, yes, you're very close. I'll be right back.

566
00:47:31,473 --> 00:47:32,804
罗马的电话通了，您可以通话了
Rome on the line. You may speak.

567
00:47:32,874 --> 00:47:33,898
您好，是的.
Hello, yes!

568
00:47:34,976 --> 00:47:36,466
你要找陆纱? 对
- Do you want Luisa? - Yes.

569
00:47:36,545 --> 00:47:39,639
你个禽兽，你不害臊嘛? 我是 罗瑟拉
Feeling guilty, you beast? This is Rossella.

570
00:47:39,714 --> 00:47:42,547
嗨，罗瑟拉，你好嘛 陆纱在找我
Hi, Rossella. How are you? Luisa was looking for me.

571
00:47:42,617 --> 00:47:46,644
你这次又跑那去了? 治疗?真会编...
Where were you this time? Your rest cure? What an excuse...

572
00:47:46,721 --> 00:47:48,552
陆纱来了
Here comes Luisa.

573
00:47:49,758 --> 00:47:52,056
贵度，我打过电话给你，你在那?
Guido, I called you twice. Where were you?

574
00:47:52,127 --> 00:47:53,856
我刚知道，真对不起
I know. I'm sorry.

575
00:47:53,929 --> 00:47:56,830
我在工厂这，在开工
I was up in the production office. We're working.

576
00:47:57,032 --> 00:47:57,999
你还好么?
How are you?

577
00:47:58,066 --> 00:48:00,728
还不错...那治疗进展如何?
Not bad... And the treatment?

578
00:48:00,802 --> 00:48:02,929
有点作用了.
Is it helping?

579
00:48:03,004 --> 00:48:06,804
也许吧，但是，你知道 我还不能好好休息
Perhaps. But, you know, I can't really rest.

580
00:48:07,008 --> 00:48:08,532
你呢?在忙什么? 过得好么?
And you? What are you doing? Having fun?

581
00:48:08,710 --> 00:48:12,339
还是老样子.我和罗瑟拉在一起，还有 泰裕恩科.他们正要走呢
The usual. I'm with Rossella, Tilde, Enrico. They were about to leave.

582
00:48:12,414 --> 00:48:14,848
那你过得好么? 找到你的红颜知己了么
But are you having a good time? Did you meet anybody?

583
00:48:14,916 --> 00:48:16,645
好难啊.我觉得不太可能了
Hardly. It's a terrible bore.

584
00:48:16,718 --> 00:48:18,618
但是为了工作，只能这样了
But for my work, it's better this way.

585
00:48:18,687 --> 00:48:19,813
晚安吧，贵度 晚安
- Good night, Guido. - 'Night.

586
00:48:20,789 --> 00:48:24,657
你没和谁约会吧? 你总是这样一个人么?
You've met no one you know? Are you always alone?

587
00:48:24,726 --> 00:48:26,057
就是这样的
Of course.

588
00:48:26,461 --> 00:48:27,723
真的么?
Really?

589
00:48:28,797 --> 00:48:31,561
陆纱，你来我这散散心吧
Luisa, why don't you come visit?

590
00:48:32,000 --> 00:48:33,695
来住几天. 况且过来也很方便
Just a short stay. It's easy to get here.

591
00:48:33,735 --> 00:48:35,999
你什么时候开始拍摄， 现在很无聊么?
When are you going to start shooting, you bore?

592
00:48:36,037 --> 00:48:38,130
我还不知道. 还是让我和陆纱说吧
I don't know. Let me talk to Luisa, please.

593
00:48:38,406 --> 00:48:40,772
那，我真的可以去么? 你想让我去么?
So, should I come? Do you want me to?

594
00:48:40,842 --> 00:48:42,434
我当然想了
If you'd like to.

595
00:48:42,911 --> 00:48:44,640
你还可以带个朋友一起来
You could even bring a friend.

596
00:48:44,713 --> 00:48:45,941
这样好么?
But would it make you happy?

597
00:48:46,014 --> 00:48:48,346
当然好了，要不我也不会让你过来
Of course, or I wouldn't ask you.

598
00:48:48,583 --> 00:48:50,608
先生，您还要继续通话么? 不了
- Sir, are you staying on? - No.

599
00:48:50,652 --> 00:48:52,449
我该什么时候过去呢?
When should I come?

600
00:48:52,520 --> 00:48:53,748
随时都可以
Whenever it's good for you.

601
00:48:53,822 --> 00:48:55,255
小心咯，我真的要来了
Careful, I'll come.

602
00:48:55,323 --> 00:48:57,223
亲爱的，那还犹豫什么，来吧
Darling, I wouldn't have asked.

603
00:48:57,292 --> 00:48:59,886
我很想... 迫不及待了，晚安吧
I'd love it... So long, and good night.

604
00:48:59,961 --> 00:49:01,553
再见了，远方的先生.晚安
Bye, Mr. Alienated. Good night.

605
00:49:03,064 --> 00:49:04,292
晚安，贵度
Night, Guido.

606
00:49:12,440 --> 00:49:14,738
晚安，绅士
Monsieur Guido, my agent thought...

607
00:49:14,809 --> 00:49:17,642
等一下，夫人.我刚进办公室
Just a second, madam. I am going to step into the office so...

608
00:49:17,712 --> 00:49:20,112
天啊! 这可是我最喜欢的
- Shit! - It's in my best interest.

609
00:49:20,181 --> 00:49:22,308
明天早上我们再仔细谈吧 好吗?
Tomorrow morning we'll discuss everything. All right?

610
00:49:28,757 --> 00:49:32,124
主要结构：10,000
Beams for the central structure:. 1 0,000.

611
00:49:32,594 --> 00:49:35,358
地上的木板：260
Planks for steps: 260.

612
00:49:35,797 --> 00:49:36,821
晚上
'Evening.

613
00:49:37,165 --> 00:49:37,824
您需要点什么呀?
Do you need something?

614
00:49:37,899 --> 00:49:39,457
没什么，谢谢了. 不打扰您工作了
No, thanks. Go on with your work.

615
00:49:40,635 --> 00:49:43,126
你们这支摄影组还很有凝聚力么
What a well-behaved production team.

616
00:49:45,106 --> 00:49:46,266
嗨
Hi.

617
00:49:46,474 --> 00:49:48,442
哦，嗨 依蕾莫拉
Oh, hi Eleonora.

618
00:49:48,943 --> 00:49:52,709
钢材：2，350
2,350. Corrugated iron.

619
00:49:52,781 --> 00:49:54,442
听着，多特拉，正好你也在
Listen, Dottore, since you're here.

620
00:49:54,516 --> 00:49:57,747
我打电话那德国人打电话，可她已经走了
I called the pensione about the German, but she's gone.

621
00:49:57,819 --> 00:49:59,719
你必须找到她 她现在和一个马戏团在巴黎
- You must find her. - She's in Paris with a circus.

622
00:49:59,788 --> 00:50:00,914
真的嘛?
Really?

623
00:50:06,428 --> 00:50:07,952
我该怎么作呢?
What should I do?

624
00:50:09,898 --> 00:50:11,365
这是我的荣幸，多特里
What an honor, Dottore.

625
00:50:11,433 --> 00:50:13,264
让你捉歼在床了
You've caught me with my pants down!

626
00:50:13,868 --> 00:50:17,668
听着贵度. 农场的事...是这样的...
Listen Guido. About the farm... there's that...

627
00:50:18,206 --> 00:50:20,834
看这，这是那里啊?
Ah, here. Where's this place?

628
00:50:22,243 --> 00:50:24,575
连地址都没写，什么都没有
It doesn't even have a note about the address, nothing!

629
00:50:24,913 --> 00:50:26,608
这是属于王子的
It's in the Prince's estate.

630
00:50:26,781 --> 00:50:28,612
谁在里面那? 是我的侄女么
- Who's in here? - My little nieces.

631
00:50:29,484 --> 00:50:31,042
依瓦和蒂娜
Eva and Dina.

632
00:50:31,486 --> 00:50:32,714
- 晚上 -
'Evening.

633
00:50:34,422 --> 00:50:35,912
来，让导演看看你
C'mon. Let him take a look at you.

634
00:50:35,990 --> 00:50:38,481
也许他会给你一点戏呢
Perhaps he'll give you a little part.

635
00:50:40,428 --> 00:50:41,827
很高兴见到你 荣幸之至
- Nice to meet you. - My pleasure.

636
00:50:42,931 --> 00:50:43,989
你从那里来的?
Where are you from?

637
00:50:44,799 --> 00:50:47,461
的里雅斯特 [意大利东北部港市] 意大利万岁!
- Trieste. - Hurray for ltaly!

638
00:50:50,371 --> 00:50:52,202
你布置的还不错呀
You've got a nice set up here, don't you?

639
00:50:52,407 --> 00:50:53,396
跟他聊聊我的表弟
Tell him about my cousin.

640
00:50:53,475 --> 00:50:56,740
贵度.这个是我的表弟 6尺高了
Guido. This one's cousin is six feet tall.

641
00:50:56,811 --> 00:50:58,938
你该认识认识她 也许可以安排个角色给她呢
You should see her. She might be good for the movie.

642
00:50:59,080 --> 00:51:00,513
这个么...像个恶女啊
This one... you she-devil...

643
00:51:00,648 --> 00:51:04,379
真的.她和我站在床上一样高那
It's true. She's tall like me standing on the bed.

644
00:51:04,519 --> 00:51:05,884
哦?
See?

645
00:51:06,020 --> 00:51:07,817
她获得过两次尼龙袜小姐呢
She's twice been voted Miss Nylon Stockings.

646
00:51:07,956 --> 00:51:09,821
贵度在这么?我进来了
Is Guido in there? I'm coming in.

647
00:51:09,958 --> 00:51:11,755
睡吧，克诺其雅，快睡觉 明早见
Sleep, Conocchia, sleep. I'll see you tomorrow.

648
00:51:12,193 --> 00:51:14,252
我能问你个问题么?
May I ask you a question?

649
00:51:14,662 --> 00:51:15,594
说吧
Go ahead.

650
00:51:15,730 --> 00:51:20,827
我的朋友说... 你拍不了爱情片
My friend here says... you can't make a love story.

651
00:51:20,869 --> 00:51:22,496
住嘴 她说得很对
- Shut up! - She's right.

652
00:51:24,305 --> 00:51:25,533
要我明早叫你起来么?
Should I wake you up in the morning, Guido?

653
00:51:25,673 --> 00:51:26,571
不了，谢谢你
No, thanks.

654
00:51:30,712 --> 00:51:32,703
我们头从来没抓到过我们偷懒
Our commander will never catch us unprepared.

655
00:51:32,847 --> 00:51:34,678
这些工作组从来不休息的
This production crew never sleeps!

656
00:51:34,816 --> 00:51:36,750
头好痛.我这是吃什么了?
Such a splitting headache. What did I eat?

657
00:51:38,586 --> 00:51:40,713
虽然有时候他们也胡闹 可是本质却不坏
They're always horsing around, but they're good guys.

658
00:51:40,789 --> 00:51:44,122
你还需要什么，贵都 这是你的新创意么
Do you need anything, Guido? Is it a new idea?

659
00:51:44,192 --> 00:51:45,625
有事要跟我说么
Do you have something to tell me?

660
00:51:45,693 --> 00:51:47,490
不了，谢谢你，没什么
No, thank you, no.

661
00:51:47,562 --> 00:51:49,291
快回去睡觉吧 我不需要什么了
Go back to bed. I don't need anything.

662
00:51:49,364 --> 00:51:51,025
