Man's inner confusion. But you've got to be clearer.

836
01:10:42,296 --> 01:10:45,527
你自己一定要十分清楚 要不就没有意义了
You have to make yourself understood. Otherwise what's the use of it?

837
01:10:48,201 --> 01:10:50,169
