Tell him everything.

853
01:12:23,864 --> 01:12:25,661
都认了吧，别再隐瞒了
Confess everything, don't hide anything

854
01:12:25,732 --> 01:12:29,190
你要是还有时间，也跟我聊聊
and if you have any spare time just put in a good word for me too.

855
01:12:29,936 --> 01:12:33,269
这可天赐良机，贵都 那可是教主啊，你太幸运了
It's a golden opportunity, Guido. The Cardinal! You're so lucky.

856
01:12:33,340 --> 01:12:35,672
