Remember my divorce in Mexico City. Get me my Mexican divorce.

858
01:12:38,578 --> 01:12:40,011
他不会拒绝你的
He won't say no to you.

859
01:12:40,080 --> 01:12:43,106
忏悔之前，记得跪下
And above all show you're devout, throw yourself down on your knees,

860
