主可以帮助你们解脱
There's no salvation outside the church.

870
01:13:47,881 --> 01:13:51,373
让主来帮你解脱
Extra Ecclesiam, nemo salvatur.

871
01:13:52,619 --> 01:13:55,782
出了教堂你就会全部解脱
No one will meet salvation, outside the church.

872
01:13:58,291 --> 01:14:02,455
