25,000 很好，有人出到24,000了
25,000? Very well, the bid is 24,000.

881
01:15:25,478 --> 01:15:27,275
还有没有人出30,000
Do I hear 30,000?

882
01:15:27,347 --> 01:15:33,115
太好了35,000...40,000 加油啊，快要得到了....
Splendid. 35,000... 40,000. Going, going...

883
01:15:33,186 --> 01:15:38,624
最后一次竞价! 50,000 50,000块成交!
One more offer? 50,000, the bid is 50,000...

884
01:15:59,646 --> 01:16:01,773
你来多久了? 有5天了吧
- When did you get here? - Around five.

885
01:16:01,848 --> 01:16:03,475
我去过酒店了，可你不在
We went to the hotel, but you weren't there.

886
01:16:04,517 --> 01:16:05,984
你还好嘛? 好，很好
How are you? - Fine, fine.

887
01:16:07,921 --> 01:16:08,945
你和谁来的?
Who did you come with?

888
01:16:09,022 --> 01:16:11,582
罗瑟拉和恩瑞克，泰迪也来了
With Rossella and Enrico. Tilde's here too.

889
01:16:16,329 --> 01:16:19,127
我的宝贝，你终于是来了 你知道么，看起来挺好
Good girl. You actually came. You look good, you know?

890
01:16:21,368 --> 01:16:22,528
嗨，罗萨
Hey there, Rossa.

891
01:16:22,669 --> 01:16:25,797
我们很久没跳舞了，一年?
It's been a year since we last danced together.

892
01:16:28,408 --> 01:16:31,275
陆纱，亲爱的，你对我很珍贵
Luisa, darling. You're my treasure.

893
01:16:31,645 --> 01:16:35,012
你能来我真高兴 永远都是
I'm so happy you came. It's always the same.

894
01:16:35,081 --> 01:16:37,914
你一离开我就...
As soon you're away...

