Thanks.

912
01:17:37,043 --> 01:17:40,479
麦斯，我们随时效劳 我们可以开始么?
Maestro, we're at your service. Should we get going?

913
01:17:40,547 --> 01:17:41,809
我来了
I'm coming.

914
