919
01:17:55,895 --> 01:17:57,658
她是你的精神向导啊!
Your guiding spirit.

920
01:17:57,731 --> 01:18:00,029
我们有那么亲密么?
Haven't you reached that stage of intimacy yet?

921
01:18:00,100 --> 01:18:02,864
我能介绍我的姐妹给你么 真可爱的妹妹
- May I introduce my sister? - Ah, the beautiful little sister!

922
01:18:02,936 --> 01:18:05,928
大导演，你很有吸引力嘛
You see the kind of women your director attracts?

923
01:18:06,005 --> 01:18:07,267
幸会幸会
Delighted to meet you, Commendatore.

924
01:18:07,307 --> 01:18:10,037
我刚拍了一部核战争的片子
I just finished a screenplay about nuclear warfare.

925
01:18:10,110 --> 01:18:12,670
只有你这样有胆识的制作人才能做到
Only a producer of your courage could get it made.

