and one night her portrait suddenly changed its expression.

941
01:18:58,958 --> 01:19:00,721
来，上车吧
Please, get in.

942
01:19:00,794 --> 01:19:03,388
好像预示着某种危险
Changed as if it wanted to warn me about some danger...

943
01:19:03,430 --> 01:19:04,920
我做前面吧
I'll sit in the front.

944
01:19:05,965 --> 01:19:08,627
几天后，我的叔叔说...
So a couple days later my uncle says,

945
