我们去市场吧，孩子们
Let's go to the market, kid.

946
01:19:10,336 --> 01:19:14,397
我觉得这是某种先兆
He drove an lsotta Fraschini... I was recounting a premonition...

947
01:19:41,066 --> 01:19:43,227
