这呢，监督
Here, Commendatore.

952
01:19:56,548 --> 01:19:58,072
我们要准备好第20个
We've gotta be ready for the 20th.

953
01:19:58,517 --> 01:20:01,509
跟我来，女士们 小心点，路不太平坦
Follow me, ladies. Careful. The ground is bumpy.

954
01:20:01,987 --> 01:20:06,253
我们得进度有点落后了 不是得，我们已经到70公里了
It seems to me we're a bit behind. - No. We're already up to 70 meters.

955
01:20:06,324 --> 01:20:07,450
你说，陆纱这是怎么了?
Listen, what's up with Luisa?

956
