She's changed all of a sudden. She's turned so nervous and angry.

957
01:20:09,995 --> 01:20:12,361
我想是因为看到你太激动了吧
I don't know. She was so happy to come see you.

958
01:20:12,431 --> 01:20:14,023
你可能说了一些让她难过得事.
You might have said something that upset her.

959
01:20:14,066 --> 01:20:16,159
不可能. 那么这又是什么?
- Never. - And what's this?

960
01:20:16,234 --> 01:20:18,498
我对这个格外地着迷.
I find this extraordinarily fascinating.

961
01:20:18,570 --> 01:20:22,165
这个模型很有层次感
This model will be superimposed on the structure,

962
01:20:22,240 --> 01:20:24,470
有一触即发的感觉.
to create the illusion that the rocket is on the launch pad.

963
01:20:24,509 --> 01:20:25,908
对嘛? 对的.
- Am I right? - Right.

964
01:20:28,246 --> 01:20:30,009
这就是触发它的平台.
This is the rocket's launch pad.

965
01:20:30,082 --> 01:20:32,516
是整部电影的精华
The most important moment in the movie.

966
01:20:34,386 --> 01:20:36,684
不许拍照. 就一个，监督.
No photos. - Just one, Commendatore.

967
01:20:37,522 --> 01:20:40,491
你丈夫现在在忙什么啊?写科幻小说?
What is your husband up to this time? Science fiction?

968
01:20:41,093 --> 01:20:43,323
我怎么知道?你问他.
What do I know? Ask him.

969
01:20:43,562 --> 01:20:46,292
Giancarlo给他写了个非常美妙的关于火星人的故事.
Giancarlo wrote him such a beautiful story about Martians.

970
01:20:47,866 --> 01:20:49,834
这个游乐园是干什么用的?
What is this amusement park for?

971
01:20:49,901 --> 01:20:51,994
你根本不了解这需要多少的工作量.
You have no idea what a job this was.

972
01:20:52,070 --> 01:20:55,369
没有一家建筑公司愿意接下它
No construction company wanted to take it on.

973
01:20:55,440 --> 01:20:57,135
它整个都要修筑在沙子上.
It rests entirely on sand.

974
01:20:57,209 --> 01:20:59,734
它需要多少的混凝土多少?
How much concrete did it take?

975
01:21:00,145 --> 01:21:04,013
非常多!400吨.
Tons! 400 tons.

976
01:21:04,082 --> 01:21:06,175
监督，如果你不介意
Commendatore, if you don't mind,

977
01:21:06,251 --> 01:21:09,152
我不想再爬楼梯了，我有点头晕.
I'll stop at the end of this first flight. I have vertigo.

978
01:21:09,454 --> 01:21:12,150
八千万你可以至少可以买10座公寓.
For 80 million you could buy at least ten apartments.

979
01:21:12,224 --> 01:21:14,920
有点华而不实，和他一样
It's a pompous shack, just like him.

980
01:21:15,994 --> 01:21:18,588
你这女孩对你的导演姐夫一点也不客气啊
The little sister-in-law is not exactly tender with our director.

981
01:21:18,663 --> 01:21:20,324
没准她看上导演了 啊?
Maybe she's in love with him. - With him?

982
01:21:20,398 --> 01:21:23,094
我整天都在祈祷能有个这样的丈夫呢
I pray day and night that I'll be spared a husband like him.

983
01:21:23,335 --> 01:21:24,927
怎么? 还得爬楼梯啊!
What now? More climbing?

984
01:21:25,003 --> 01:21:26,595
我倒是很乐意背你上去
I'd be glad to carry you.

985
01:21:26,905 --> 01:21:31,399
这建筑可是花费不菲啊
When I think he made me spend 80 million on this structure.

986
01:21:31,476 --> 01:21:34,445
要是有个好的布景就锦上添花了
Wouldn't a well-crafted backdrop have been better?

987
01:21:34,846 --> 01:21:37,713
布景?那一点也不新鲜
A backdrop! That's out of your grandfather's time.

988
01:21:37,782 --> 01:21:39,841
克诺斯雅，就这也花费了几百万么?
Besides, are they your millions, Conocchia?

989
01:21:42,254 --> 01:21:46,315
陆纱，冷不冷? 穿上我的衣服
Luisa, are you cold? Take my jacket.

990
01:21:46,391 --> 01:21:48,325
没关系，我不冷
No, no. Thank you.

991
01:21:48,393 --> 01:21:50,156
那好吧，反正我们也快回酒店了
Anyway, we're going back to the hotel.

992
01:21:53,498 --> 01:21:55,022
那里不对么?
Is something wrong?

993
01:21:55,100 --> 01:21:59,935
怎么郁郁不乐啊
You've gotten sad all of a sudden. Am I wrong?

994
01:22:00,839 --> 01:22:04,138
我没有啊
No. I'm not sad at all.

995
01:22:08,413 --> 01:22:10,711
首先开始的是地球的画面
The sequence starts with an image of planet Earth

996
01:22:10,782 --> 01:22:13,979
然后看到是核爆发时候的蘑菇云
completely wiped out by a thermonuclear war...

997
01:22:14,219 --> 01:22:17,848
贵都，见到你很高兴 真的
Guido seemed glad to see you, really.

998
01:22:17,889 --> 01:22:22,223
...剩余的人类试图乘坐飞船逃跑
...and the spaceship, our new Noah's Ark, tries to escape, while the rest of humanity

999
01:22:22,294 --> 01:22:25,058
到其他星球上避难
seeks refuge on another planet.

1000
01:22:25,130 --> 01:22:28,622
十万，越来越多的人开始聚集
More than 1 0,000 extras, even 1 5,000, a tragic crowd.

1001
01:22:30,402 --> 01:22:33,462
电影里真的有这么壮观的场面么?
We're really going to see all this in your movie?

1002
01:22:33,772 --> 01:22:38,334
有个领袖开始大声喊着 他想吸引大家的注意
The prophet is raising his voice. He's decided to scare everybody.

1003
01:22:38,410 --> 01:22:41,470
当然了，电影就要标新立异才能吸引观众
Why not? Don't tell me you also love movies where nothing happens?

1004
01:22:42,380 --> 01:22:44,610
我的电影更是要这样
In my movie I have all sorts of things happen.

1005
01:22:45,584 --> 01:22:48,610
我尽量注入更多的元素
I'm putting everything in. Even a tap-dancing sailor.

1006
01:22:49,521 --> 01:22:51,011
赛拉，过来这
Sailor, come here.

1007
01:22:51,089 --> 01:22:53,114
你也会说美国话了?
What did you learn in America?

1008
01:22:53,158 --> 01:22:55,786
不是，我不喝水 跳段舞看看，我给你安排点戏
No, I don't want water. Dance and I'll give you a part.

1009
01:22:57,095 --> 01:22:58,323
跳吧
Dance.

1010
01:23:06,504 --> 01:23:08,631
你这是怎么了?
What's up with you? What's going on?

1011
01:23:08,707 --> 01:23:12,108
罗斯卡，可别这么教训我了 让我一点心情都没了
Rossella, cut the big sister tone. It puts me off right away.

1012
01:23:13,845 --> 01:23:16,370
大导演先生，我打算给我演什么呢
Mr. Director, what part do I get?

1013
01:23:22,187 --> 01:23:24,519
陆纱怎么看我啊?她想干什么呢?
What does Luisa think about me? What does she want to do?

1014
01:23:25,056 --> 01:23:26,956
我演什么呢?您想好了么?
What's my part? My part?

1015
01:23:27,158 --> 01:23:28,250
别捣乱!
Go away!

1016
01:23:29,461 --> 01:23:31,156
你了解陆纱的.她话不多
You know Luisa. She doesn't say much.

1017
01:23:31,229 --> 01:23:32,856
我是她最好的朋友，她的话也不多
Not even to me, and I'm her best friend.

1018
01:23:33,465 --> 01:23:37,128
我真的不懂她
I really don't know. She's lost.

1019
01:23:37,202 --> 01:23:39,261
今天这样，明天那样，从来都没谱
One day she says one thing, another day, something else.

1020
01:23:40,472 --> 01:23:42,804
可是，她对你
Unfortunately, I think the only thing she'd like

1021
01:23:43,141 --> 01:23:44,938
却从来没改变过
is for you to be someone else.

1022
01:23:45,277 --> 01:23:46,403
为什么?
Why?

1023
01:23:46,478 --> 01:23:48,844
这也是人之常情么
It's the mistake everyone makes.

1024
01:23:51,283 --> 01:23:55,811
我看那傻小子是不是有点喜欢她啊
But that kind little fellow, is he in love with her?

1025
01:23:56,087 --> 01:23:59,318
你喜欢这样么，你的内心是这么想的么?
You'd like that, so your conscience won't gnaw at you anymore.

1026
01:24:00,191 --> 01:24:01,988
你个混蛋
You're such a scoundrel.

1027
01:24:02,594 --> 01:24:07,691
可怜的恩瑞克，他好奇怪 可不是我一个人这么说
Poor Enrico, he's so awkward. Everybody's noticed.

1028
01:24:08,233 --> 01:24:10,997
陪她走走，多顺着她点
He hangs around, listens to her, keeps her company.

1029
01:24:11,569 --> 01:24:13,036
他人很不错的
He's a great friend.

1030
01:24:17,175 --> 01:24:19,006
我想我的思路还是很清晰的
I thought my ideas were so clear.

1031
01:24:20,378 --> 01:24:23,745
我想做点真实的电影 不蒙骗观众
I wanted to make an honest film. No lies whatsoever.

1032
01:24:24,916 --> 01:24:29,080
我要说的就就是...
I thought I had something so simple to say.

1033
01:24:30,388 --> 01:24:32,413
对每个人都有意义的
Something useful to everybody.

1034
01:24:32,557 --> 01:24:34,821
能名垂千史的
A film that could help to bury forever

1035
01:24:34,959 --> 01:24:37,757
这样的才有价值
all those dead things we carry within ourselves.

1036
01:24:40,432 --> 01:24:44,425
事实上，这样才能让我充满激情
Instead, I'm the one without the courage to bury anything at all.

1037
01:24:45,937 --> 01:24:51,375
现在我好困惑 这开关是控制...
And now I'm utterly confused. This launch pad to deal with...

1038
01:24:54,479 --> 01:24:56,743
我为什么总是感觉不对
I wonder why things turned out this way.

1039
01:24:59,017 --> 01:25:01,247
是那里出错了呢
When did I go wrong?

1040
01:25:04,122 --> 01:25:06,249
我无话可说了...
I really have nothing to say...

1041
01:25:07,292 --> 01:25:09,192
其实我说还是老毛病
but I want to say it all the same.

1042
01:25:11,529 --> 01:25:14,521
你的意思是，为什么救援队伍不来么?
And your spirits, why don't they come to my rescue?

1043
01:25:15,100 --> 01:25:17,466
你总说他们有很多要对我说
You always said they had plenty of messages for me.

1044
01:25:17,736 --> 01:25:19,465
告诉他们少说多做
Let them get to work!

1045
01:25:19,671 --> 01:25:23,266
我提醒过你注意自己的态度
I've already told you, your attitude is wrong,

1046
01:25:23,341 --> 01:25:26,003
你对他们太严厉了
Your curiosity toward them is childish.

1047
01:25:26,511 --> 01:25:28,445
你总是要万无一失
You want too many guarantees.

1048
01:25:28,513 --> 01:25:32,244
好了，他们到底怎么说的? 总是有麻烦事
- Fine, but what do they say? - Always the same thing. Even now.

1049
01:25:33,284 --> 01:25:35,912
他们做的也很好的 对你的需要也了如指掌
They're very reasonable spirits. They know you very well.

1050
01:25:36,788 --> 01:25:38,119
哪有怎样?
So?

1051
01:25:39,824 --> 01:25:43,590
他们说你天马行空 你也该有点条理了
They say you're free, but you must learn to choose.

1052
01:25:44,162 --> 01:25:48,258
你时间不多了，抓紧点吧
You don't have much time. And you have to hurry.

1053
01:25:51,136 --> 01:25:55,402
贵都，你过来么? 到底来不来?
Guido, are you coming up? Yes or no?

1054
01:26:43,288 --> 01:26:44,550
请到320房间来
Room 320, please.

1055
01:26:44,722 --> 01:26:45,916
没人在啊
Nobody's in.

1056
01:26:46,658 --> 01:26:47,852
好的，谢谢
Fine, thanks.

1057
01:27:30,969 --> 01:27:32,129
你头痛了吧
Have you got a headache?

1058
01:27:33,171 --> 01:27:34,638
恩，吃了点阵痛片
No, it's a tranquilizer.

1059
01:27:35,406 --> 01:27:36,600
常吃这个?
Do you take them often?

1060
01:27:38,343 --> 01:27:39,867
有时候吧，失眠的时候吃
Sometimes, to help me sleep.

1061
01:27:43,314 --> 01:27:44,838
你就别担心我了
What's worrying you now?

1062
01:28:09,908 --> 01:28:10,897
恩?
What?

1063
01:28:11,276 --> 01:28:13,369
没什么，你要好好照顾自己
Nothing. If you could only see yourself.

1064
01:28:14,078 --> 01:28:15,409
笑什么呢?
Why are you laughing?

1065
01:28:15,747 --> 01:28:19,274
我可没想过背叛你，就算我看不惯你
I don't think I could ever betray you, if only because I couldn't bear

1066
01:28:19,350 --> 01:28:24,310
欺骗多么可笑啊
the ridiculous effort of having to hide and lie.

1067
01:28:24,789 --> 01:28:26,654
对你来说太容易了
But obviously it's easy for you.

1068
01:28:27,458 --> 01:28:30,916
听着，陆纱.我真高兴你能来
Listen Luisa. I am very happy you're here,

1069
01:28:31,396 --> 01:28:34,661
我已经精疲力尽了
but I am very tired and sleepy.

1070
01:28:39,037 --> 01:28:42,473
睡会儿吧，晚安
Sleep then. Good night.

1071
01:28:49,047 --> 01:28:52,539
我不知道你怎么看我的
I don't know what you think my life is like, reducing it all

1072
01:28:52,617 --> 01:28:54,881
变成别人希望的那样
to the pettiness of somebody stealing from the cookie jar.

1073
01:28:54,986 --> 01:28:58,513
你了解我什么呢?我的喜好你知道么
What do you know about my life? What I hate and what I don't.

1074
01:28:58,856 --> 01:29:00,551
我只了解我看到的
I only know what you show me.

1075
01:29:04,896 --> 01:29:06,591
那我是什么样的?
What am I showing you?

1076
01:29:07,632 --> 01:29:09,031
说吧，你觉得我是什么样的人
Come on, tell me what you see.

1077
01:29:09,901 --> 01:29:12,893
说说你的道德标准
You and your judgmental moralism. What are you getting at?

1078
01:29:13,037 --> 01:29:16,837
没什么，我们好久没有倾心的聊聊了
Nothing. I know we've been stagnating for years.

1079
01:29:17,542 --> 01:29:20,136
这都是因为你；你总是不让我说
But it's you; you're the one who always calls me back

1080
01:29:20,211 --> 01:29:21,872
所以我们才没机会
and wants to start all over again.

1081
01:29:22,680 --> 01:29:25,012
我只求你这一次，不要再重新开始了
Once and for all, I don't want to restart anything.

1082
01:29:25,483 --> 01:29:26,745
那该怎样?
But what do you want?

1083
01:29:27,285 --> 01:29:30,652
你要我来一定有原因吧 说说看
Why did you want me here? What good am I to you?

1084
01:29:30,989 --> 01:29:33,651
为什么要我来，我能帮你点什么呢?
What are you trying to get from me? What is it you want?

1085
01:30:54,405 --> 01:30:58,501
别烦，我昨晚已经去的时候已经找到她了
Don't fret. I'd already spotted her last night when I got in.

1086
01:31:07,485 --> 01:31:09,919
我没问，她也没提起
I've asked no questions, so don't say a word.

1087
01:31:10,088 --> 01:31:14,081
你就是要我听你撒谎来的么?
Spare me the embarrassment of having to listen to your lies.

1088
01:31:18,696 --> 01:31:20,755
她长的真可爱
She must have been born in March or April.

1089
01:31:20,798 --> 01:31:23,961
她一定是个白羊座的，典型的
She's got all the characteristics of an Aries. She's the Aries type.

1090
01:31:24,001 --> 01:31:26,231
还是我来告诉你吧
I'll tell you what type she is.

1091
01:31:26,571 --> 01:31:30,098
将来绝对是个可塑之材
Exactly the type most likely to make

1092
01:31:30,141 --> 01:31:34,805
一个没有个性和主见的人
a good companion for feeble, spineless, confused men.

1093
01:31:35,880 --> 01:31:37,871
陆纱，我不明白
Luisa, I didn't know.

1094
01:31:38,416 --> 01:31:41,681
我和你一样，也是第一次见到她
I'm seeing her for the first time, like you.

1095
01:31:42,587 --> 01:31:45,351
真的，就像这里一样，很多人
Really, in a place like this, where there are so many people,

1096
01:31:45,423 --> 01:31:48,551
她处境也不好，不用很奇怪
it's no surprise to run into the poor thing.

1097
01:31:50,728 --> 01:31:53,595
难怪你从昨晚开始就折磨我
So this is why you've been tormenting me since last night.

1098
01:31:53,998 --> 01:31:55,590
你也应该说清楚嘛
You should have told me.

1099
01:31:58,202 --> 01:32:00,898
最让我接受不了的是
What annoys me most is that people could think

1100
01:32:00,972 --> 01:32:02,735
人们认为我只接触有品味的人
I'd go with somebody who dresses that way.

1101
01:32:03,441 --> 01:32:04,772
你怎么知道她的品味的?
Have you seen her clothes?

1102
01:32:04,842 --> 01:32:06,673
我们走走好吗
Listen, can't we go for a walk?

1103
01:32:06,744 --> 01:32:08,268
还是换个话题吧
Let's not talk about this anymore.

1104
01:32:08,346 --> 01:32:11,042
这三年来你总是这样 好了，够了!
It's been over for three years. Finished. Enough.

1105
01:32:14,118 --> 01:32:17,986
你快让我疯了 他装正经的
He drives me crazy. He pretends he's telling the truth.

1106
01:32:18,055 --> 01:32:21,821
他的诚实都是虚伪的 觉得自己总是对的
He acts honest. As if he's the one who's right.

1107
01:32:23,361 --> 01:32:25,386
你怎么能接受这些呢?
How can you live this way?

1108
01:32:27,698 --> 01:32:29,165
这么活着多累啊
It's not right living this way,

1109
01:32:29,233 --> 01:32:31,633
对谁都没有句真心话
not letting others know what's true and what's false.

1110
01:32:31,702 --> 01:32:34,432
你能不能改变一下呢? 你到底能不能改改啊?
Is it possible that for you it's all the same? How?

1111
01:32:34,472 --> 01:32:37,805
你说的对，我是很乏味
You're right. I know, I'm boring.

1112
01:32:39,143 --> 01:32:43,170
这样的生活难道你不痛苦么
How sad having to play the bourgeois wife who doesn't understand.

1113
01:32:43,815 --> 01:32:45,908
那你说，我该怎样好?
You tell me, what should I do.

1114
01:32:46,117 --> 01:32:47,914
我其实不该取笑你的
I really can't laugh about it the way you do.

1115
01:32:47,985 --> 01:32:49,953
亲爱的，我不是取笑你的
No darling, I'm not laughing.

1116
01:32:52,456 --> 01:32:55,050
你跟她说了什么啊?
What do you tell her?

1117
01:33:00,097 --> 01:33:03,498
最让我难以忍受的是，你把她带进我们的生活
What disgusts me the most is that you've mixed her up in our life.

1118
01:33:03,568 --> 01:33:06,093
她知道我和你的一切
She knows everything about you and me.

1119
01:33:07,271 --> 01:33:10,536
这婊子，真可恶!
That whore. Cow!

1120
01:33:13,678 --> 01:33:16,272
你的痛苦你自己清楚
You're a real pain, you know.

1121
01:33:24,188 --> 01:33:25,587
还有...
And yet...

1122
01:33:48,880 --> 01:33:51,542
斯格诺拉 卡尔拉，你唱歌真的很动听
Signora Carla, you sing so well.

1123
01:33:51,716 --> 01:33:53,479
那只是业余爱好罢了
No, I'm just an amateur.

1124
01:33:53,618 --> 01:33:55,051
你看上去还是那么迷人
And how pretty you look.

1125
01:33:56,220 --> 01:33:59,121
我一直都想一睹尊容 真的
I've wanted to meet you for so long. - And l, you.

1126
01:34:06,030 --> 01:34:07,588
你可真够时髦的了
You're so stylish.

1127
01:34:07,632 --> 01:34:11,762
不，你才是真正时髦的呢 我?事实上，很随便的
No, you're the stylish one. Me, frankly, I'm a bit trashy.

1128
01:34:11,836 --> 01:34:13,571
开什么玩笑，这再普通不过了
What are you talking about? This is so refined.

1129
01:34:13,571 --> 01:34:14,469
你也喜欢嘛?
Do you like it?

1130
01:34:14,505 --> 01:34:16,598
这是我在一个时装展览上找到的 是吗!
It's a little outfit I found in Vogue. - Really?

1131
01:34:16,641 --> 01:34:18,632
你要知道我可花费了不少心思
If you only knew how long it took me to find it.

1132
01:34:18,676 --> 01:34:21,270
可你不知道，如果卡尔拉要是喜欢她就会...
But you know, when Carla wants something...

1133
01:34:35,026 --> 01:34:37,358
他到了!
Here he comes!

1134
01:34:37,428 --> 01:34:40,192
贵都来了
Guido's here.

1135
01:34:41,098 --> 01:34:42,725
晚上好，女士
Good evening, women.

1136
01:34:42,800 --> 01:34:45,064
快关上门，外面有暴风!
Close the door, there's a storm.

1137
01:34:46,304 --> 01:34:47,999
你还好吗?感觉怎么样?
How are you? Well?

1138
01:34:48,072 --> 01:34:49,801
礼物上都有你们的名字
Every gift comes with its nametag.

1139
01:34:50,207 --> 01:34:52,505
别弄混了，这是卡塔锐娜的
Don't get mixed up. This is Caterina's.

1140
01:34:53,611 --> 01:34:55,135
他太可爱了
He's a darling!

1141
01:34:55,379 --> 01:34:57,677
这个是姐夫给你的
And this one is for my darling sister-in-law,

1142
01:34:57,715 --> 01:35:00,650
因为她越来越善解人意了
because she's finally understood how things should be.

1143
01:35:00,851 --> 01:35:02,443
我们这就给你放水洗澡
We'll draw your bath right away.

1144
01:35:02,520 --> 01:35:04,351
格劳瑞，这就是你想要的
Gloria, this is you-know-what.

1145
01:35:04,422 --> 01:35:07,414
谢谢.贵度，待会儿我想跟你谈谈
Thanks. I need to talk to you, Guido.

1146
01:35:08,159 --> 01:35:10,423
我知道她想说什么
I know what she wants to tell you.

1147
01:35:10,494 --> 01:35:12,985
我们得把她支开了 因为她已经开始吃醋了
Now we'll have to send her away because she's acting jealous.

1148
01:35:13,264 --> 01:35:15,596
我们在楼上说什么来着?
What were you doing upstairs?

1149
01:35:15,666 --> 01:35:19,602
我猜到她想说什么了 这个角色非我莫属了
I went to see those poor things. They'd always be alone, if not for me.

1150
01:35:19,637 --> 01:35:23,129
对她不合适，她根本就不适合演这个角色
The role doesn't suit her. She's only a common bourgeoise.

1151
