It has been a wonderful evening.

1311
01:45:52,436 --> 01:45:53,869
你怎么可以伤心呢
You mustn't be sad.

1312
01:45:56,039 --> 01:45:57,165
你来点什么喝的?
Do you need anything?

1313
01:46:01,545 --> 01:46:06,448
她们待会儿都会睡了 我还要收拾一下
Now they'll all go to bed and I still have a lot to do:

1314
01:46:08,418 --> 01:46:16,883
洗衣服，刷碗，还要擦地板
the laundry, all the dishes, mend the sheets, scrub the floors

1315
01:46:17,628 --> 01:46:20,096
然后还要准备明天的早餐
and set up breakfast for tomorrow.

1316
01:46:26,903 --> 01:46:29,371
我们大家住在一起不是很好么
Aren't we fine living all together this way?

1317
01:46:31,642 --> 01:46:34,543
起先我也不太理解
At first I didn't understand,

1318
01:46:35,579 --> 01:46:38,480
可事实都已经这样了
that this is the way things are meant to be.

1319
01:46:39,182 --> 01:46:41,241
现在已经...
But now...

1320
01:46:41,418 --> 01:46:44,387
你看我不是很好么? 我不会给你添麻烦了
Don't you think I'm good now? I don't bother you anymore.

1321
01:46:44,454 --> 01:46:45,944
我不会再问你问题了
I don't ask questions.

1322
01:46:49,826 --> 01:46:54,559
有点晚了 20年了，我才明白
A bit slow, wasn't l? It's taken me 20 years to understand.

1323
01:46:55,132 --> 01:46:59,228
我都结婚20年了，才有今天
20 years since the day we got married

1324
01:47:01,038 --> 01:47:04,201
你是我的丈夫，我是你的妻子
and you became my husband and I your wife.

1325
01:47:06,343 --> 01:47:09,312
你还记得么，记得我们结婚那天么
Do you remember Guido? Do you remember that day?

1326
01:47:12,382 --> 01:47:15,545
如果你再多一点耐心
If you could only be patient a little longer, Luisa.

1327
01:47:16,653 --> 01:47:18,450
你可能早就明白了
But perhaps you've had it.

1328
01:47:19,189 --> 01:47:23,182
事实上，我真的想听听更多的意见
Frankly, I'd love to be able to offer a word of advice.

1329
01:47:23,593 --> 01:47:25,857
可是今晚，你全部都解决了
But I think tonight you're called

1330
01:47:25,929 --> 01:47:30,161
事实上根本就没有答案
to solve a problem for which there is no solution.

1331
01:47:30,233 --> 01:47:33,600
给每个人都找到一个位置
Finding a precise face for a crowd of characters

1332
01:47:33,670 --> 01:47:37,731
有的人生是那么肤浅，平淡，乏味!
that in your script are so rough, so vague, so superficial...

1333
01:47:38,909 --> 01:47:40,342
我们看的是什么片子?
What is it we're watching?

1334
01:47:40,844 --> 01:47:42,175
我不知道，只是个片断吧
I don't know... screen tests.

1335
01:47:43,480 --> 01:47:44,640
你觉得不好么
You're not well.

1336
01:47:44,715 --> 01:47:46,478
完全相反，我觉得还不错
Quite the contrary.

1337
01:47:52,856 --> 01:47:55,484
阿哥斯蒂娜，走段猫步再加上点舞蹈
Agostini, get on the catwalk and do a little dance for us.

1338
01:47:55,559 --> 01:47:58,187
我用钢琴给你伴奏
I'll accompany you on the piano.

1339
01:47:58,995 --> 01:48:00,826
听这段， “孤独的岁月
Listen here. "The solitary ego

1340
01:48:00,897 --> 01:48:03,866
一直在重复，从不间断，
that revolves around itself and feeds upon itself, ends up

1341
01:48:03,934 --> 01:48:06,732
结局总是哭泣，或者狂笑”
strangled by a great cry or a great laugh."

1342
01:48:07,104 --> 01:48:10,665
这段是他在意大利流浪的时候写的
Words that Stendhal wrote during his stay in ltaly.

1343
01:48:10,974 --> 01:48:14,137
如果我们再多一点点幻想
If we sometimes read those sayings on chocolate wrappers

1344
01:48:14,177 --> 01:48:17,510
而不是盲目的听，就能体会里面的意境
instead of throwing them away, we would be spared many an illusion.

1345
01:48:47,677 --> 01:48:51,613
终于找到他了. 原来在门旁边准备逃跑呢
There he is. By the door, always ready to run away.

1346
01:48:55,786 --> 01:48:58,118
大家晚上好，让你们就等了
Good evening to you all and apologies for the delay.

1347
01:48:58,688 --> 01:49:00,451
现在要来点什么呢?
Well, what are you up to now?

1348
01:49:01,258 --> 01:49:02,691
贵都在那? 我在这呢!
- Guido where are you? - Here.

1349
01:49:02,759 --> 01:49:04,784
下来! 还是让我在这吧
- Come down. - I'd rather stay up here.

1350
01:49:04,861 --> 01:49:08,422
晚上好，原来你也在 我们开始吧
Evening... Good, you're here too. Let's get going.

1351
01:49:08,498 --> 01:49:09,624
马上开始
Right away.

1352
01:49:09,933 --> 01:49:12,595
他们取消了今晚所有的活动让我们用场地
They skipped the variety act tonight so we could use the theater.

1353
01:49:14,604 --> 01:49:15,502
好，开始
Let's go.

1354
01:49:16,640 --> 01:49:18,164
年轻人，是时候觉醒了
Young man, it's time to make up your mind.

1355
01:49:19,009 --> 01:49:20,704
我把所有的剪辑带过来了
I've brought all the screen tests...

1356
01:49:20,777 --> 01:49:23,610
你说什么克诺斯雅，刚才你说什么?
Pardon me Conocchia, but the time for his jokes is over.

1357
01:49:23,980 --> 01:49:26,005
他的所有猜疑，都是幻想而已
All his doubts, his uncertainties, his whims.

1358
01:49:26,082 --> 01:49:29,142
他已经有足够时间准备 我们今晚就来作出选择吧
He had all the time he wanted, but tonight we're here to choose.

1359
01:49:29,219 --> 01:49:31,119
这就是为什么我们来这 是啊
- That's why we're all here. - Right.

1360
01:49:31,188 --> 01:49:32,849
克诺斯诺已经得到他想要的一切
Conocchia has gotten everything from Rome.

1361
01:49:32,923 --> 01:49:36,256
前后所有的剪接片断，甚至5个月前拍的都给他了
The new and the old screen tests, even the ones we shot five months ago.

1362
01:49:36,526 --> 01:49:39,222
就让我们一个个的看 然后说：
Now we'll go through them one by one, and you have to say:

1363
01:49:39,262 --> 01:49:41,526
那个是妻子，那个是情人
This is the wife, this is the mistress,

1364
01:49:41,598 --> 01:49:43,896
那个是教主，你们清楚了嘛?
this is the Cardinal, this is Saraghina. Clear?

1365
01:49:44,467 --> 01:49:47,527
我可不想让整个意大利电影界笑话
I don't want to be the joke of the ltalian film industry

1366
01:49:47,604 --> 01:49:49,629
最主要的我不想让你们失望
but above all I don't want you to end up that way.

1367
01:49:50,373 --> 01:49:51,931
他们都开始抨击你了
They're all ready to shoot you down.

1368
01:49:52,309 --> 01:49:55,244
你还有几个朋友在支持你，一个都没有
You've got very few friends left, on the Left or the Right.

1369
01:49:55,312 --> 01:49:58,281
只有我在一直日日夜夜的帮助你
But I am here to help you each and every way.

1370
01:49:58,481 --> 01:50:00,949
我们必须，而且马上重新开拍
We must start shooting and we must do it immediately.

1371
01:50:01,017 --> 01:50:02,450
放片子吧
Roll the screen tests.

1372
01:50:05,589 --> 01:50:07,454
奥林帕小姐的片断
Miss Olimpia's screen test.

1373
01:50:09,226 --> 01:50:10,318
奥林帕小姐的...
Miss Olimpia...

1374
01:50:13,096 --> 01:50:18,159
要关门么? 好的，关上吧
- Should I shut the door? - Yes. Sway, sway your big hips.

1375
01:50:18,835 --> 01:50:21,929
把东西放下
Put down your stuff. Good.

1376
01:50:22,172 --> 01:50:26,336
现在到镜子那去，欣赏一下自己
Now go to the mirror. Admire yourself.

1377
01:50:27,477 --> 01:50:33,438
继续，挺起你的胸 就是这样
More. Swell your chest. There.

1378
01:50:33,717 --> 01:50:36,777
走到电话那 慢一点，不要太快
Now go to the phone. Slowly. Don't run.

1379
01:50:36,920 --> 01:50:39,354
你不要跑! 我没跑啊
- Why are you running? - I'm not.

1380
01:50:39,689 --> 01:50:42,021
好，走到这，到地板上的标记这
Look, hit that mark. There, on the floor.

1381
01:50:43,693 --> 01:50:45,991
你好，我找下门卫
Hello, the concierge please?

1382
01:50:46,329 --> 01:50:47,523
这就是
Speaking.

1383
01:50:47,597 --> 01:50:50,896
给我送杯水来
I'd like a bottle of flat water.

1384
01:50:50,967 --> 01:50:51,934
开水么?
Fiuggi.

1385
01:50:52,002 --> 01:50:53,492
不，开水太热
No, Fiuggi is sparkling.

1386
01:50:53,570 --> 01:50:57,006
往这里看! 水没有那么热
No, look this way. Fiuggi is the least sparkling.

1387
01:50:57,240 --> 01:50:58,707
那好吧
Fine, I'll take the Fiuggi.

1388
01:50:58,775 --> 01:51:00,436
这个怎样?贵都
Will this one do, Guido?

1389
01:51:00,543 --> 01:51:03,478
她能不能改变主意， 不要离别英格兰
He's got to make up his mind because she's leaving for England.

1390
01:51:03,546 --> 01:51:05,173
她下周才走呢，贵都
She's leaving next week, Guido.

1391
01:51:05,248 --> 01:51:06,716
这位是谁啊? 你别插嘴!
- And who's this one? - Shut up, you!

1392
01:51:06,716 --> 01:51:08,616
你喜欢这个演员么?
Or do you prefer this one.

1393
01:51:08,685 --> 01:51:09,777
这可是个重要的角色
This is an important character.

1394
01:51:09,853 --> 01:51:12,583
观众的第一印象就应该非常好 对吧，贵都
People need to like her right off the bat. Right, Guido?

1395
01:51:16,092 --> 01:51:17,992
斯格诺拉，累了就坐下吧
Signora, sit down as if you were drained.

1396
01:51:18,061 --> 01:51:20,154
这个女性角色，失去了挑战生活的勇气
This character is a woman who has lost the desire to fight.

1397
01:51:20,230 --> 01:51:22,926
因为...说你的台词
because... say your line...

1398
01:51:23,667 --> 01:51:24,531
一直不停么? 什么?
- Without stopping? - What?

1399
01:51:24,601 --> 01:51:26,228
真的不停么? 对，是的
- Without stopping? - Yes, yes.

1400
01:51:29,773 --> 01:51:32,207
你可以完全自由发挥
I am the one who's offering you complete freedom.

1401
01:51:33,543 --> 01:51:36,307
总之，这样对你不好的 我其实并不惹人喜欢
Anyway, I'm no good to you this way. I'm just a nuisance.

1402
01:51:41,251 --> 01:51:43,378
这位是谁? 她代表谁呢?
And who's this? What should she represent?

1403
01:51:43,987 --> 01:51:46,046
你听不到么? 她是你的老婆
Didn't you hear? She's the wife.

1404
01:51:50,226 --> 01:51:53,957
别停，她很可爱，充满热情 你是这么认为么?
Still, she's likable, soulful. Don't you think?

1405
01:51:54,597 --> 01:51:57,760
给我支烟 我也没有了，恩力克帮我们买盒烟去
- Gimme a cigarette. - I've run out. Enrico, fill us up.

1406
01:51:58,501 --> 01:52:00,366
我这有 哦，谢谢
- Here you go. - Thank you.

1407
01:52:00,437 --> 01:52:01,301
别客气
You're welcome.

1408
01:52:03,239 --> 01:52:04,672
我不能这样活下去了
I cannot go on like this any longer.

1409
01:52:04,741 --> 01:52:07,073
现在，你告诉我，我该是什么样的
Now, you tell me how I should be.

1410
01:52:07,143 --> 01:52:09,441
做一个永远不对别人撒谎，欺骗的人
Not someone who lies and swears he's telling the truth

1411
01:52:09,512 --> 01:52:11,173
哪怕一会儿
every second of the day.

1412
01:52:11,247 --> 01:52:14,045
这样的要求你做的到么? 你从来都做不到
That would be enough. You don't even do that.

1413
01:52:14,351 --> 01:52:16,945
和你在一起，我从来都没有知道过真相
With you I never, never know the truth.

1414
01:52:17,387 --> 01:52:18,854
一点点的小事你也欺骗
Even in the smallest things.

1415
01:52:20,357 --> 01:52:22,382
陆纱，那是因为我考虑你的感受
Luisa, I care for you.

1416
01:52:23,026 --> 01:52:24,721
撒谎对你太平常了
Lying is like breathing to you.

1417
01:52:24,928 --> 01:52:26,020
请再说一次
Repeat that, please.

1418
01:52:26,363 --> 01:52:27,955
撒谎对你太平常了
Lying is like breathing to you.

1419
01:52:29,632 --> 01:52:31,031
你是个厚颜无耻的人
So brazen.

1420
01:52:34,604 --> 01:52:36,333
他的生活一直都是这样 没错
- All lines from his life. - Right.

1421
01:52:36,940 --> 01:52:40,307
我认识她，还是个公主呢
I know this one. She's the princess.

1422
01:52:41,044 --> 01:52:43,239
我不是已经一个人了么? 你还能给我什么呢?
Am I not alone already? What are you giving me?

1423
01:52:43,947 --> 01:52:45,244
我还能企盼什么呢?
What have I got to look forward to?

1424
01:52:45,315 --> 01:52:47,078
看这边，然后戴上眼镜
Look this way. Put on the glasses.

1425
01:52:48,518 --> 01:52:50,110
重复最后一句的台词
Repeat the last line.

1426
01:52:50,186 --> 01:52:51,778
我难道不是一个人么?
Am I not alone already?

1427
01:52:51,855 --> 01:52:53,755
你一定要说么 对，一定要说
You have to say it, yes, aggressively,

1428
01:52:53,823 --> 01:52:55,381
再掺杂点感情
but also with deep bitterness.

1429
01:52:55,825 --> 01:52:58,555
他说：什么? 你要分开?
He said:. What? You want a separation.

1430
01:52:58,628 --> 01:52:59,720
你要一个人么?
You want to be alone.

1431
01:52:59,896 --> 01:53:01,796
你一个人怎么生活啊?
But what would you do on your own?

1432
01:53:01,831 --> 01:53:05,961
她回答说：为什么不? 我不是已经一个人了么?  照着说
And she answers:. why, am I not alone already? Go on.

1433
01:53:07,070 --> 01:53:09,868
贵都，从来都不要怀疑，她是个完美的女人
Guido, there's no doubt about this one. She's perfect.

1434
01:53:15,945 --> 01:53:18,641
5个月.我们都分开5个月了
Five months. We've been going this way for five months.

1435
01:53:18,982 --> 01:53:20,472
可是她们都老了啊
But they're all so old!

1436
01:53:22,819 --> 01:53:23,877
水好了
Fiuggi is sparkling.

1437
01:53:23,953 --> 01:53:27,013
不，这水一点也不热 “大声点说”
No, it's the least sparkling. Louder.

1438
01:53:29,492 --> 01:53:30,652
好，放下电话
Put down the phone.

1439
01:53:31,761 --> 01:53:33,388
奥莉帕的片断
Screen test for Miss Olimpia.

1440
01:53:34,731 --> 01:53:35,993
这个怎样?
What about this one?

1441
01:53:36,066 --> 01:53:40,799
离开我你会很危险的
It's dangerous leaving me alone.

1442
01:53:42,138 --> 01:53:43,833
为什么，你干什么了?
Why, what do you do?

1443
01:53:43,907 --> 01:53:45,101
我要再说一次么?
Should I repeat the line?

1444
01:53:45,175 --> 01:53:51,080
不用了，把你的头转过来一点点 好，停!
No, just turn your little head this way. Now, stop.

1445
01:53:52,215 --> 01:53:53,876
你要去哪里?
Where are you going?

1446
01:53:55,418 --> 01:53:56,942
当然是回酒店，我好困了!
Back to the hotel. I'm sleepy.

1447
01:53:57,320 --> 01:53:59,288
等等，听我说
Wait a second. Listen.

1448
01:53:59,856 --> 01:54:01,289
发生什么事了么?
What happened?

1449
01:54:01,458 --> 01:54:04,950
没什么，我们之间也发生不了什么了
Nothing. Nothing ever happens between us.

1450
01:54:06,596 --> 01:54:08,530
你看到什么不开心的事了么?
Were you offended by something you saw?

1451
01:54:09,032 --> 01:54:09,862
只是拍电影而已
It's just a movie.

1452
01:54:09,999 --> 01:54:11,796
我是第一个醒悟的
I'm the first to understand that.

1453
01:54:11,868 --> 01:54:14,894
电影，只是个新的发明罢了，骗人的机器
It's a movie, another invention, another lie.

1454
01:54:14,971 --> 01:54:17,599
你把所有的感情放进去，都变成你希望的那样
You put everybody in it, but the way you like to see them.

1455
01:54:17,674 --> 01:54:19,539
可我知道真相!
But I know the truth.

1456
01:54:19,609 --> 01:54:23,545
不同的是我不会去
The difference is that I would never have the impudence

1457
01:54:23,613 --> 01:54:25,171
告诉别人你的厚颜无耻了!
to tell everybody the way you do.

1458
01:54:25,949 --> 01:54:28,042
去拍你的电影吧!
Go ahead. Make your movie.

1459
01:54:28,118 --> 01:54:29,176
不，我不会
No, I won't.

1460
01:54:29,252 --> 01:54:31,152
再放纵我自己，任你们的自私滋长
Indulge yourself. Stroke your ego.

1461
01:54:32,355 --> 01:54:34,721
你能告诉大家你很伟大
Go make everyone think you're so wonderful.

1462
01:54:35,158 --> 01:54:38,150
可是你不能告诉人们
What could you ever teach strangers when you can't

1463
01:54:38,228 --> 01:54:40,662
你最真实的一面
even tell the simplest truth to the ones closest to you?

1464
01:54:40,697 --> 01:54:42,426
我们永远看到的你真实的那一面
To the one who's been growing old with you?

1465
01:54:42,465 --> 01:54:44,126
好了陆纱，别说这些了
Come on Luisa. Cut the drama.

1466
01:54:46,169 --> 01:54:48,103
你叫我来是对的
You were right to ask me here.

1467
01:54:48,838 --> 01:54:51,272
我们该结束了
We needed to find closure.

1468
01:54:51,574 --> 01:54:54,099
这次，我保证不会再回心转意了
This time, I assure you, I won't be coming back.

1469
01:54:54,477 --> 01:54:56,104
你可以去死了
You can go to hell!

1470
01:55:09,058 --> 01:55:12,459
好吧，走吧，走吧!
Fine, just run, run.

1471
01:55:12,962 --> 01:55:15,157
你快走吧
Do what the doctor ordered, run!

1472
01:55:15,231 --> 01:55:19,998
闭嘴!把这个无知的人赶走!
Shut up! Throw this ignoramus out.

1473
01:55:20,570 --> 01:55:22,060
好了，你快唱吧
Fine, now sing.

1474
01:55:22,772 --> 01:55:25,400
你可能以为我弄错了 可是帐单还在没结...
You may say I'm losing it, but I have the bills here...

1475
01:55:26,543 --> 01:55:30,809
让我付这个，做梦! 克诺斯雅，你做梦去吧
I'll never pay this one, never! Conocchia, you're losing it.

1476
01:55:31,281 --> 01:55:33,841
萨拉娜看，我们有钱了
Saraghina look, we've got the money.

1477
01:55:34,551 --> 01:55:36,917
萨拉娜，跳舞吧，跳伦巴吧!
Saraghina, the Rumba, the Rumba...

1478
01:55:37,086 --> 01:55:40,021
贵都，说点什么吧，求求你了
Guido, would you please say something? Please!

1479
01:55:42,058 --> 01:55:43,355
这个合格么，贵都?
What about this one, Guido?

1480
01:55:44,561 --> 01:55:46,392
我还是喜欢前面那个
Frankly I preferred the one before.

1481
01:55:47,130 --> 01:55:48,427
这人是南方来的
This one is from Naples.

1482
01:55:48,498 --> 01:55:52,594
你看不出来我...很烦么?
Can't you see that I'm... stuttering.

1483
01:55:52,936 --> 01:55:56,201
你什么时候开始，我已经等烦了
When are you coming? I'm tired of waiting.

1484
01:55:56,372 --> 01:55:57,202
看着我的眼睛
Look at me.

1485
01:55:57,273 --> 01:55:59,468
不要离开我，我好怕
Don't leave me alone! You know it's dangerous.

1486
01:55:59,842 --> 01:56:04,506
不要离开我，我需要依靠，亲爱的
Don't leave me alone. You know it's dangerous, darling.

1487
01:56:04,647 --> 01:56:05,511
看这边!
Look over here.

1488
01:56:05,648 --> 01:56:08,947
你怎么还不来? 不要让我再等待了
Why aren't you coming now? Why are you keeping me waiting?

1489
01:56:09,319 --> 01:56:11,378
你知道让我在这等是不安全的
You know it's dangerous when I have to wait.

1490
01:56:11,454 --> 01:56:13,649
大声，再大声点儿，行不行啊
Louder, louder!

1491
01:56:14,190 --> 01:56:16,124
伯爵夫人，继续走
Countess, walk.

1492
01:56:18,461 --> 01:56:19,655
不要碰我
Don't touch me.

1493
01:56:19,729 --> 01:56:21,754
这边来，到这边
This way, this way.

1494
01:56:24,133 --> 01:56:26,601
格瑞斯小姐，片断一
Screen tests Mrs. Grazia, one.

1495
01:56:26,970 --> 01:56:28,528
露出你的肩来，要快!
Just bare your shoulders all of a sudden.

1496
01:56:28,605 --> 01:56:31,506
萨拉娜，我们有钱了，有钱了!
Saraghina, we've got the money. The money.

1497
01:56:32,475 --> 01:56:34,705
停，非常好.可以通过么?
Stop. Very good. Was it all right?

1498
01:56:36,846 --> 01:56:39,406
斯诺格拉，你看可以么?
Signora, what do you think?

1499
01:56:39,482 --> 01:56:41,313
如果都不表态，我们看还有什么意义
If he won't speak up, at least we can say something.

1500
01:56:41,384 --> 01:56:44,717
都说说意见，我们很民主的嘛，对不对?
Somebody say something! This is a democracy, right?

1501
01:56:47,190 --> 01:56:50,421
你不要躲了，呵呵，还好嘛?
You can't hide. We've found you anyway. How are you?

1502
01:56:50,760 --> 01:56:53,752
我是勃利迪，是珂劳迪亚的经纪人
Hi, I'm Poletti, from Claudia's press agency.

1503
01:56:53,830 --> 01:56:57,027
15年前见过的，不过您可能不记得了
We met 1 5 years ago. You might not remember me...

1504
01:56:57,100 --> 01:56:59,762
看，她过来了 那呢?
- Look, she's here. - Where?

1505
01:57:06,442 --> 01:57:07,704
失陪一下
Excuse me.

1506
01:57:16,753 --> 01:57:19,221
珂劳迪亚，你好吗?
- Claudia. - How are you?

1507
01:57:19,289 --> 01:57:23,089
还不错，谢谢 你终于来了
Well, and you? You're finally here.

1508
01:57:23,259 --> 01:57:24,487
我们出去聊聊，可以吗?
Let's go outside, all right?

1509
01:57:25,295 --> 01:57:27,263
这是卡罗琳，我的女秘书
This is Caroline, my secretary.

1510
01:57:30,033 --> 01:57:31,557
我想和你单独谈谈
I'd like to talk to you alone.

1511
01:57:37,340 --> 01:57:38,807
我们什么时候开拍?
When do we start shooting?

1512
01:57:39,275 --> 01:57:41,869
快了，马上 我的那部份剧本呢
- Soon, very soon. - And what's my part?

1513
01:57:42,645 --> 01:57:43,873
我等会儿会告诉你的
I'll tell you everything later.

1514
01:57:43,946 --> 01:57:45,811
真高兴能和你合作
I'm very happy to be working with you

1515
01:57:45,882 --> 01:57:47,281
我希望能帮上你的忙
and I hope I'll be able to help you.

1516
01:57:47,617 --> 01:57:48,914
快跟我讲讲
But you must tell me everything.

1517
01:57:50,386 --> 01:57:51,580
我们这是去哪?
Where are we going now?

1518
01:58:01,564 --> 01:58:05,056
哦，是这边
Well? - This way.

1519
01:58:22,118 --> 01:58:24,484
你真的太漂亮了 任何语言在你面前都显得苍白
You're so beautiful. I'm at a loss for words.

1520
01:58:24,554 --> 01:58:26,249
你让我心跳不已，像个孩子一样
You make my heart beat like a school boy's.

1521
01:58:27,990 --> 01:58:29,082
你不信我吗，嗯?
You don't believe me, do you?

1522
01:58:30,360 --> 01:58:32,658
是你让我重新燃起对生命的激情
You inspire such deep respect.

1523
01:58:33,563 --> 01:58:37,192
你爱的是谁? 珂劳迪亚，你喜欢我么?
Who do you love? Claudia, who are you with?

1524
01:58:37,266 --> 01:58:39,131
我最关心的是谁? 当然是你啊
- Who do you care for? - You.

1525
01:58:42,305 --> 01:58:44,000
知道么，你来的太是时候了
You arrived just in time, you know.

1526
01:58:45,508 --> 01:58:47,169
你在坏笑什么?
Why do you smile that way?

1527
01:58:47,243 --> 01:58:50,610
我连想都不敢想你会这么看我 不要嘲讽我了
I never know if you're judging me, absolving me, mocking me.

1528
01:58:50,680 --> 01:58:53,672
我想听听你的意见，告诉我 你怎么看这部电影
I'm listening. You said you wanted to tell me about the film.

1529
01:58:53,750 --> 01:58:55,081
其实我不懂什么
I don't know anything.

1530
01:59:01,224 --> 01:59:04,990
你能不能先把别的事放一放 然后我们从头来说
Could you leave everything behind and start from zero again?

1531
01:59:06,396 --> 01:59:09,490
一件一件事聊 我们好好探讨一下
Pick one thing, and one only, and be absolutely devoted to it?

1532
01:59:09,799 --> 01:59:11,994
我们生存的意义
Make it the reason for your existence,

1533
01:59:12,068 --> 01:59:14,400
是因为世间的人和事是互相关联的
the thing that contains everything, that becomes everything,

1534
01:59:14,437 --> 01:59:18,066
只要我们认真去做好每一件事，就会成功的 你能做到么?
because your dedication to it makes it last forever? Could you?

1535
01:59:19,542 --> 01:59:22,602
好，听着，如果我问你，珂劳迪亚...
All right, listen. If I were to say, Claudia...

1536
01:59:25,381 --> 01:59:27,576
今后你打算怎么办? 我不知道该怎么办...
Where are we going? I don't know the way...

1537
01:59:28,785 --> 01:59:31,219
你会怎么说?
And what about you? Could you?

1538
01:59:32,188 --> 01:59:35,783
春天已经不远了 看着我，转过来
The springs must be nearby. Listen. Turn here.

1539
01:59:38,294 --> 01:59:40,421
你眼前的我，决不会
No, this guy here, he couldn't.

1540
01:59:41,030 --> 01:59:44,488
放弃任何人和事，他要抓住一切机会
He wants to grab everything, can't give up a single thing.

1541
01:59:45,301 --> 01:59:46,359
他每天都在进步
He changes his mind every day,

1542
01:59:46,436 --> 01:59:48,563
因为他不想和成功擦肩而过
because he's afraid he might miss the right path.

1543
01:59:48,638 --> 01:59:50,731
他会这样一直追求到底 这就是这部电影的结局么?
And he's slowly bleeding to death. - So this is how the movie ends?

1544
01:59:50,773 --> 01:59:52,070
不，这是电影的开始
No, this is how it starts.

1545
01:59:52,175 --> 01:59:54,143
他会碰到一个如春天一样美丽的姑娘
Then one day he meets the girl of the spring.

1546
01:59:54,210 --> 01:59:56,974
她会给人们带来希望
She's one of those girls that distributes the healing water,

1547
01:59:57,980 --> 02:00:04,442
她是一个美丽，善良，淳朴的女人
she's beautiful, young and ancient, a child and a woman already,

1548
02:00:04,520 --> 02:00:09,287
真实而又饱满 她绝对可以拯救心灵
authentic and radiant. There's no doubt that she's his salvation.

1549
02:00:10,893 --> 02:00:12,690
你又着披肩长发，穿着洁白的裙子
You'll be dressed in white and your hair will be long,

1550
02:00:12,762 --> 02:00:14,286
就象你现在穿的一样
just the way you wear it.

1551
02:00:24,841 --> 02:00:26,274
把灯关了吧
Turn the headlights off.

1552
02:01:05,181 --> 02:01:06,307
然后呢?
And then?

1553
02:01:21,764 --> 02:01:23,129
我们离开这里
Let's leave.

1554
02:01:25,067 --> 02:01:28,161
可我不喜欢这，不够真实
I don't like this place. It doesn't feel real.

1555
02:01:29,038 --> 02:01:31,199
我喜欢大的场景，这有点奇怪么?
I like it enormously. Isn't that odd?

1556
02:01:34,710 --> 02:01:37,611
我还不能体会你的意境
I didn't get much from your story.

1557
02:01:38,414 --> 02:01:42,373
这个角色很像你自己 一个不会真正去爱的人
A guy like your character, who doesn't love anybody,

1558
02:01:42,685 --> 02:01:44,346
是不会轻易坠入爱河的
is not very sympathetic you know.

1559
02:01:46,489 --> 02:01:49,754
这是他的错，他还能想得到什么?
It's his fault. What does he expect?

1560
02:01:51,260 --> 02:01:53,125
你以为我真的不懂么?
You think I don't know that?

1561
02:01:54,230 --> 02:01:56,755
你真的是顽固不化
You're a bit of a bore too.

1562
02:01:57,099 --> 02:01:59,932
难道一点批评都不能接受?
You really can't take the least bit of criticism.

1563
02:02:00,169 --> 02:02:03,798
你戴那顶帽子太好玩了，像个老头子一样
You're so funny with that big hat, made up like an old man.

1564
02:02:06,576 --> 02:02:11,343
我不明白.他需要一个女人带给他全新的生活
I don't understand. He meets a girl that can give him a new life

1565
02:02:11,847 --> 02:02:13,314
又把她推走?
and he pushes her away?

1566
02:02:13,382 --> 02:02:15,077
是因为他不再相信...
Because he no longer believes in it.

1567
02:02:16,686 --> 02:02:18,551
他自己会真的去爱一个人
Because he doesn't know how to love.

1568
02:02:18,788 --> 02:02:21,120
他相信没有任何女人可以改变他
Because it isn't true that a woman can change a man.

1569
02:02:21,490 --> 02:02:23,048
事实上他根本不懂得爱
Because he doesn't know how to love.

1570
02:02:23,125 --> 02:02:26,617
总之我觉得这次很真实
And above all because I don't feel like telling another pile of lies.

1571
02:02:26,796 --> 02:02:28,696
因为他真的不懂得爱
Because he doesn't know how to love.

1572
02:02:30,366 --> 02:02:34,427
我真的抱歉 让你这么远道而来
I'm sorry, Claudia, for making you come all the way here.

1573
02:02:35,304 --> 02:02:37,465
别再虚伪了
You're such a fake.

1574
02:02:37,707 --> 02:02:39,402
电影里面根本就没有我的角色
So, there's no part in the film.

1575
02:02:40,476 --> 02:02:43,570
是啊，找不到这样的角色
You're right. There isn't.

1576
02:02:43,846 --> 02:02:47,873
事实上也没有电影 什么都没有
And there's no film. There's nothing anywhere.

1577
02:02:48,484 --> 02:02:52,079
如果我可以拿主意 我会把所有人遣散了
If it were up to me we would call it all off now.

1578
02:02:57,493 --> 02:02:59,358
哦，原来你在这呢
Ah, here you are.

1579
02:02:59,428 --> 02:03:02,693
下周就开拍了，你去了那了?
Where did you go? We're starting next week.

1580
02:03:03,966 --> 02:03:05,695
你的制片人有个好的打算
Your producer had a great idea.

1581
02:03:05,768 --> 02:03:08,760
准备办个舞会庆祝开拍
The greatest cocktail party ever to launch a movie.

1582
02:03:08,838 --> 02:03:10,863
那你知道在那么? 明天下午，午饭的时候
And you know where? - At the launch pad. Tomorrow afternoon.

1583
02:03:10,940 --> 02:03:12,703
电视台，广播台，还有国外记者呢
Radio, television, and all the foreign press.

1584
02:03:13,042 --> 02:03:15,237
来吧，贵都，我们要真正开始了
Come on, Guido, we're starting for real.

1585
02:03:40,703 --> 02:03:41,727
抓住他!
Catch him!

1586
02:03:49,011 --> 02:03:50,706
走，我们聊聊
Let's go. Walk!

1587
02:03:50,780 --> 02:03:51,576
我要回家了!
I want to go home.

1588
02:03:51,647 --> 02:03:54,138
这呢，他在这呢
Here, he's here.

1589
02:04:02,992 --> 02:04:04,755
贵都你去那?这没事了 别走啊
Guido, where are you going? It's over here.

1590
02:04:10,733 --> 02:04:13,258
贵都，今天一定是个伟大的时刻
Guido, I'm sure today will be a beautiful day.

1591
02:04:19,375 --> 02:04:22,435
我对你的构思非常好奇...
I'm really curious to finally hear the story...

1592
02:04:23,913 --> 02:04:27,144
你是不是过于自爱了，安瑟门先生?
Don't you take yourself a little too seriously, Mr. Anselmo?

1593
02:04:34,590 --> 02:04:36,956
别烦我，我自己可以走
Leave me alone, I can walk by myself.

1594
02:04:42,031 --> 02:04:44,226
祝你成功!
Good luck!

1595
02:04:47,269 --> 02:04:49,464
多特瑞，原来你在这儿
Dottore, here he is!

1596
02:04:52,341 --> 02:04:53,968
安静!
Calm down!

1597
02:04:54,043 --> 02:04:56,807
我们都等你这么长时间了，快冷场了啊
We've been waiting three days for you. It's winter already.

1598
02:04:57,213 --> 02:04:58,544
请安静!
Attention, please.

1599
02:05:04,420 --> 02:05:07,878
您认为色情也是艺术的分支么, 或者...
...do you think of pornography as an art form or...

1600
02:05:07,957 --> 02:05:10,425
或者色情会打破传统的...
...is pornography a more intense form of...

1601
02:05:10,493 --> 02:05:14,054
您为什么从来不拍爱情片?
...why don't you ever make a film about love?

1602
02:05:27,510 --> 02:05:29,068
我希望声明一下...
I wish to announce that...

1603
02:05:29,145 --> 02:05:30,874
明天...明天...
Tomorrow... tomorrow...

1604
02:05:31,213 --> 02:05:33,613
这部片子您在传达一种什么精神?
What do you think you can teach us?

1605
02:05:33,682 --> 02:05:35,741
您认为你的生活可以更加生动么?
Do you really think your life can be of any interest to others?

1606
02:05:38,053 --> 02:05:40,749
他要讲话了
He wants to say something.

1607
02:05:50,099 --> 02:05:53,227
快回答，说点什么啊，快
Answer, say something, go on.

1608
02:05:53,836 --> 02:05:57,465
什么都行，随便说也行
Anything at all! Say anything!

1609
02:05:58,340 --> 02:05:59,705
求求你了!
Do it for me!

1610
02:06:02,478 --> 02:06:03,809
我保证你...
I promise you...

1611
02:06:03,879 --> 02:06:07,610
...这部电影结束后，你想怎样都行
...this film. And afterward, what will you live on?

1612
02:06:08,918 --> 02:06:11,079
您是怎样看离婚的? 能谈谈么...
Are you for or against divorce? Tell me, frankly...

1613
02:06:11,153 --> 02:06:14,179
难道你要离婚么?
Is that your main problem?

1614
02:06:14,256 --> 02:06:16,247
您不想说，还是这只是您的借口?
That you can't communicate? Or is that just a pretext?

1615
02:06:16,492 --> 02:06:19,120
你的问题有点不太好!
Your questions betray a certain hostility.

1616
02:06:19,195 --> 02:06:21,663
我相信我走的路是正确的
I assure you my director is in great form...

1617
02:06:21,831 --> 02:06:23,628
我要怎么办?我该怎么办?
What should I do? What am I supposed to do?

1618
02:06:24,166 --> 02:06:26,396
他们该对他友好一点，因为...
...he should be treated with respect, because...

1619
02:06:26,669 --> 02:06:28,762
克诺斯雅，原谅我，如果我态度不好的话
Conocchia, forgive me if I treated you badly.

1620
02:06:29,171 --> 02:06:32,140
你是世上最伟大的人
You were wonderful, the best of them all.

1621
02:06:32,208 --> 02:06:34,199
充满了智慧和爱心
He ponders, considers, reflects.

1622
02:06:34,710 --> 02:06:35,768
请讲话!谈谈吧!
Speak! Answer!

1623
02:06:35,845 --> 02:06:37,745
我花钱就是要你做事的
I've paid for your confusion, your breakdown.

1624
02:06:37,813 --> 02:06:39,337
这几个月来我该做的都做了
For months I've been paying for everything.

1625
02:06:39,415 --> 02:06:41,576
现在退出的话我会杀了你
Quit this film and I'll ruin you.

1626
02:06:41,984 --> 02:06:43,781
他现在可以认我摆布了
He'll now be at your disposal.

1627
02:06:43,853 --> 02:06:45,184
新闻界一直...
The press always has been...

1628
02:06:45,254 --> 02:06:48,280
珂劳迪亚，你在那? 给我点鼓励吧，罗瑟拉?
Claudia, where are you? And your spirits, Rossella?

1629
02:06:50,759 --> 02:06:53,353
我该怎么做? 可以走么?
What should I do? Leave you? Disappear?

1630
02:06:53,429 --> 02:06:55,363
这次不用了
You will never be what you once were.

1631
02:06:55,631 --> 02:06:58,998
我还会是你的妻子么? 你什么时候可以和我结婚?
Will I ever be your wife? When will you truly marry me?

1632
02:06:59,168 --> 02:07:01,659
陆纱，你真的打算分手么?
Luisa, is it really true that you want a separation?

1633
02:07:01,737 --> 02:07:02,795
你舍得离开我么?
That you want to leave me?

1634
02:07:02,872 --> 02:07:04,464
我到最后还是接受不了
How can I go on like this 'til the end?

1635
02:07:04,540 --> 02:07:06,167
想想你老婆会怎么想?
...and what does your wife think?

1636
02:07:11,413 --> 02:07:13,506
在你的右边口袋里，多特里
It's in your right-hand pocket, Dottore.

1637
02:07:14,483 --> 02:07:15,677
够了，贵都
So long, Guido.

1638
02:07:15,851 --> 02:07:17,682
我放你右边口袋里了
I put it in your right-hand pocket.

1639
02:07:27,196 --> 02:07:30,825
谁都不可以带走. 布冯!
Nobody gets away with this. Buffoon!

1640
02:07:30,900 --> 02:07:34,802
滚出去，滚! 你个胆小鬼!
Out of there, out! You coward!

1641
02:07:35,771 --> 02:07:38,638
马上就好，马上! 让我想想怎么说
Just a minute, a little moment. I'm thinking of what to say.

1642
02:07:39,975 --> 02:07:42,876
我马上就来...很快的!
I'm coming... right away!

1643
02:07:45,614 --> 02:07:47,980
真是个多情的种子
Such an incurable romantic.

1644
02:07:52,488 --> 02:07:54,956
你要跑到那里去?
Where are you running, you low-life?

1645
02:08:13,175 --> 02:08:15,735
都拆了，伙计们 电影结束了
Take it all down, guys! The film is off.

1646
02:08:16,045 --> 02:08:19,105
两天内都拆了，马上开始行动
In two days it all has to be gone. Start right away.

1647
02:08:19,448 --> 02:08:20,915
都给我拆了，动手吧!
Tear it all down. Come on!

1648
02:08:21,183 --> 02:08:23,048
这就完了，多特里? 是的，十分感谢!
- Is that it, Dottore? - Yes, thanks.

1649
02:08:23,185 --> 02:08:25,983
大家保重了 下次再见吧
So long, guys. See you next time.

1650
02:08:26,322 --> 02:08:27,584
我们希望是
Let's hope so.

1651
02:08:33,028 --> 02:08:34,222
保重，赛乐!
So long, sailor.

1652
02:08:38,634 --> 02:08:40,295
你的决定是对的
You've made the right choice.

1653
02:08:40,369 --> 02:08:42,303
相信我，今天是个好的开始
Believe me, today is a good day for you.

1654
02:08:43,238 --> 02:08:45,399
这些决定不容易，我能理解
These are tough decisions, I know.

1655
02:08:45,908 --> 02:08:49,674
我们是对的，我说我们 是因为我一直在乎你的感受
But we intellectuals, and I say we because I consider you such,

1656
02:08:49,979 --> 02:08:52,675
任何时候都是一样的
must remain lucid to the bitter end.

1657
02:08:53,148 --> 02:08:55,241
生命本来就有好多疑惑
This life is so full of confusion already,

1658
02:08:55,317 --> 02:08:58,047
我们何必自寻烦恼呢
that there's no need to add chaos to chaos.

1659
02:08:59,822 --> 02:09:02,882
损失点钱其实是很正常的
Losing money is part of a producer's job.

1660
02:09:04,860 --> 02:09:07,328
我祝贺你 因为你没有办法
I congratulate you. You had no choice.

1661
02:09:07,629 --> 02:09:09,324
他却得到报应了
And he got what he deserved,

1662
02:09:09,531 --> 02:09:13,331
这么愚蠢的冲动，错误是必然的
for having joined such a frivolous venture so lightheartedly.

1663
02:09:15,371 --> 02:09:17,703
听我的，不用自责
Believe me, no need for remorse.

1664
02:09:17,973 --> 02:09:19,463
人要学会放弃
Destroying is better than creating

1665
02:09:19,541 --> 02:09:22,237
如果我们走的路是错的，就要学会放弃
when we're not creating those few, truly necessary things.

1666
02:09:22,678 --> 02:09:25,272
在这个世界上
But then is there anything so clear and right

1667
02:09:25,347 --> 02:09:27,611
没有什么事是绝对的
that it deserves to live in this world?

1668
02:09:28,984 --> 02:09:31,953
对他来说，电影失败了，也只是破财而已
For him, the wrong movie is only a financial matter.

1669
02:09:32,121 --> 02:09:35,488
对你来说，追求完美才更重要
But for you, at this point, it could have been the end.

1670
02:09:36,225 --> 02:09:38,989
放弃没什么不对，象古人一样
Better to quit and strew the ground with salt,

1671
02:09:39,061 --> 02:09:42,428
我们总有一天化作尘土，净化这个世界
as the ancients did, to purify the battlefields.

1672
02:09:42,865 --> 02:09:45,834
生命尽头，我们需要的是...
In the end what we need is...

1673
02:09:45,901 --> 02:09:49,029
纯洁的，透彻的世界
some hygiene, some cleanliness, disinfection.

1674
02:09:49,371 --> 02:09:53,831
如果我们玷污了画面，语言，声音
We're smothered by images, words and sounds

1675
02:09:53,909 --> 02:09:59,040
我们就没有权利生存，一点价值都没有了
that have no right to exist, coming from, and bound for, nothingness.

1676
02:09:59,415 --> 02:10:03,784
真的的艺术家，是不会象任何人索取什么的
Of any artist truly worth the name we should ask nothing

1677
02:10:03,852 --> 02:10:07,151
除了对艺术的追求，什么都可以不要!
except this act of faith: to learn silence.

1678
02:10:07,589 --> 02:10:10,217
还记得一本诗集上写着...
Do you remember Mallarme's homage to the white page?

1679
02:10:10,292 --> 02:10:11,589
等等，贵都
And Rimbaud... - Guido, wait!

1680
02:10:11,660 --> 02:10:14,458
把我当作朋友吧，忘了我的身份
...a poet, my friend, not a movie director. What was his finest poetry?

1681
02:10:14,530 --> 02:10:16,521
我们已经准备好了.
We're ready to begin.

1682
02:10:16,598 --> 02:10:20,090
那个作者现在已经停笔了，去非洲体验生活了
His refusal to continue writing and his departure for Africa.

1683
02:10:20,169 --> 02:10:21,466
恭喜了
Congratulations.

1684
02:10:21,537 --> 02:10:25,337
如果我们什么灵感都没有 就算拍了也一文不值
If we can't have everything, true perfection is nothingness.

1685
02:10:25,741 --> 02:10:30,678
原谅我的直言，可是批评家就要敢于说这话
Forgive me for quoting all the time. But we critics... do what we can.

1686
02:10:31,346 --> 02:10:35,442
我们的义务就是...排除一切不该有的错误
Our true mission is... sweeping away the thousands of miscarriages

1687
02:10:35,517 --> 02:10:39,977
每时每刻...都要...去寻找光明
that everyday... obscenely... try to come to the light.

1688
02:10:40,656 --> 02:10:45,116
你真的要放弃这部电影了么?
And you would actually dare leave behind you a whole film,

1689
02:10:45,661 --> 02:10:49,256
走了一半的路就要放弃了?
Iike a cripple who leaves behind his crooked footprint.

1690
02:10:49,965 --> 02:10:52,297
我真的不敢相信这是真的
Such a monstrous presumption to think

1691
02:10:52,367 --> 02:10:56,633
这么说别人不用受你的折磨了
that others could benefit from the squalid catalogue of your mistakes!

1692
02:10:57,639 --> 02:11:00,301
你这样会快乐么
And how do you benefit from stringing together

1693
02:11:00,375 --> 02:11:01,774
你难道不会后悔么?
the tattered pieces of your life?

1694
02:11:01,844 --> 02:11:04,642
你脑海里，有那些深爱着的人么
Your vague memories, the faces of people

1695
02:11:04,713 --> 02:11:06,908
还有他们的身影么?
that you were never able to love...

1696
02:11:15,591 --> 02:11:18,116
你做这个决定的时候不会哆嗦么
What is this sudden happiness that makes me tremble,

1697
02:11:18,193 --> 02:11:19,785
生命啊，给我力量吧!
giving me strength, life?

1698
02:11:21,430 --> 02:11:23,455
原谅我，亲爱的
Forgive me, sweet creatures.

1699
02:11:23,532 --> 02:11:25,466
我还是不能理解，不明白
I hadn't understood. I didn't know.

1700
02:11:26,268 --> 02:11:28,828
爱上你应该是很自然的事
It's so natural accepting you, loving you.

1701
02:11:29,171 --> 02:11:30,798
又这么简单
And so simple.

1702
02:11:31,373 --> 02:11:34,342
陆纱，我觉得自由了!
Luisa, I feel I've been freed.

1703
02:11:34,843 --> 02:11:37,038
什么事都很美好，有意义了!
Everything seems so good, so meaningful.

1704
02:11:37,112 --> 02:11:38,374
这世界开始真实了
Everything is true.

1705
02:11:38,780 --> 02:11:40,748
我希望可以释怀
I wish I could explain.

1706
02:11:41,416 --> 02:11:43,316
可不知道该怎样去
But I don't know how to.

1707
02:11:44,153 --> 02:11:48,089
事情又开始混沌了，象以前一样
So. Everything is confused again, as it was before.

1708
02:11:48,223 --> 02:11:49,087
光芒!
The lights!

1709
02:11:49,158 --> 02:11:50,716
这次，混沌的是...我
But this confusion is... me.

1710
02:11:50,792 --> 02:11:53,852
虽然不是我想要的，顺其自然吧
Not as I'd like to be, but as I am.

1711
02:11:54,329 --> 02:11:58,265
我再也不怕讲真话了
I'm not afraid anymore of telling the truth,

1712
02:11:58,333 --> 02:12:02,292
无论是我不理解的，正在寻找的，都不怕了
of the things I don't know, what I'm looking for and haven't found.

1713
02:12:02,571 --> 02:12:04,061
这样我才能活的更真实
This is the only way I can feel alive

1714
02:12:04,139 --> 02:12:06,801
我的眼睛可以诚实的看着你
and I can look into your faithful eyes without shame.

1715
02:12:07,576 --> 02:12:09,134
人生本就是个庆典
Life is a celebration.

1716
02:12:09,211 --> 02:12:10,872
我们要勇敢面对
Let's live it together!

1717
02:12:12,014 --> 02:12:14,881
这就是我要说的 陆纱， 对你也好，对别人也好
This is all I can say Luisa, to you or the others.

1718
02:12:15,017 --> 02:12:17,042
如果你还爱我，请接受我吧
Accept me for what I am, if you want me.

1719
02:12:17,419 --> 02:12:19,853
只有这样我们才能够相互接受
It's the only way we might be able to find each other.

1720
02:12:21,023 --> 02:12:22,923
我不知道你说的是不是对的
I don't know if what you said to me is right.

1721
02:12:23,659 --> 02:12:26,719
要是你帮我，我可以试试看
But I can try if you help me.

1722
02:13:26,588 --> 02:13:28,715
等一下，我就会让你们去做
Just a minute. I'll give you the go-ahead.

1723
02:13:39,334 --> 02:13:42,269
现在，都走到窗帘那
Now. Go to the curtain.

1724
02:13:51,913 --> 02:13:52,971
把它画下来
Draw it.

1725
02:13:54,950 --> 02:13:57,009
大家都下来
Everyone come down.

1726
02:13:57,085 --> 02:13:59,610
好好谈谈
Talk to each other.

1727
02:14:51,006 --> 02:14:52,098
妈妈
Mother.

1728
02:14:57,746 --> 02:15:01,147
闭嘴!我知道你要跟我说什么
Sgulp! I did understand what you wanted to say, you know.

1729
02:15:01,216 --> 02:15:03,081
你还是离不开我们的
That you can't do without us.

1730
02:15:03,518 --> 02:15:07,477
你明天什么时候给我电话? 好了，好了，现在排好队!
At what time will you call me tomorrow? - Fine, fine. Now join the line!

1731
02:15:07,522 --> 02:15:08,511
马里思
Maurice!

1732
02:15:12,728 --> 02:15:16,858
过来，快!别四处闲逛了.
Come, quickly! Stop fooling around.

1733
02:15:17,099 --> 02:15:21,798
每个人都手拉手一起转吧!
Everybody hold hands! Spread out! All together.

1734
02:15:24,406 --> 02:15:25,373
大师!
Maestro!

1735
02:15:26,007 --> 02:15:28,305
让我们跳舞吧
Let's all hold hands!

1736
02:15:29,305 --> 02:15:30,305
''八个半'' -= 剧终=-
